%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Auditor%20EY%20Faces%20Inquiry%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Accounting%20Regulator%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20accounting%20regulator%2C%20the%20National%20Financial%20Reporting%20Authority%20(NFRA)%2C%20has%20initiated%20an%20inquiry%20against%20one%20of%20EY%E2%80%99s%20member%20firms%20in%20the%20country%2C%20S.R.%20Batliboi%2C%20which%20audits%20certain%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-25%2Fadani-auditor-ey-faces-inquiry-by-india-s-accounting-regulator%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%3Ereported%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%2025).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20NFRA%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20began%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20The%20National%20Financial%20Reporting%20Authority%20has%20requested%20documents%20and%20communications%20related%20to%20the%20audits%20of%20Adani-controlled%20companies%20dating%20back%20to%202014%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ES.R.%20Batliboi%20currently%20audits%20five%20of%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20listed%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20Adani%20Power%2C%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%2C%20Adani%20Wilmar%2C%20and%20recently%20acquired%20cement%20companies%20ACC%20and%20Ambuja%20Cements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20unclear%20how%20long%20the%20NFRA%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20could%20take%20or%20what%20repercussions%2C%20if%20any%2C%20could%20be%20faced%20by%20the%20auditor%20or%20the%20audited%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloo