20that%20India%20has%20gone%20through%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%20One%20reason%20for%20this%20change%20is%20the%20fading%20memory%20of%20English%20colonialism%2C%20with%20the%20Mughals%2FMuslims%20being%20increasingly%20seen%20as%20the%20real%20colonisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20world%2C%20yet%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20change%20in%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20Hindu%20majority%2C%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20massive%20support%20for%20the%20Israeli%20war%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20coming%20from%20India.%20One%20person%20noted%20that%20it%20was%20amusing%20to%20see%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20calling%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Hebrew%20and%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20posts%20calling%20for%20the%20annihilation%20of%20Gaza%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNu8B5Jjy1is%5C%22%3Ein%20Hindi%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20may%20have%20been%20exaggerating%2C%20but%20it%20is%20true%20that%20there%20was%20an%20obscene%20glee%20in%20the%20Indian%20media%20after%20Israel%20started%20to%20bomb%20Gaza%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20surprise%20Hamas%20attack%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fpalestinian-deaths-toll-war-gaza-israel-hamas%2Farticle67423083.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520current%2520war%2520erupted%2520a%2CThe%2520overwhelming%2520majority%2520were%2520civilians.%5C%22%3Ekilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%201%2C300%20Israelis%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20and%20took%20more%20than%20200%20Israelis%20as%20hostages%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhostage-families-face-appalling-dilemma-gaza-invasion-looms-2023-10-23%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20be%20exchanged%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%205%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20including%20children%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20has%20to%20be%20fair%20to%20the%20Indian%20media.%20It%20was%20after%20all%20not%20very%20different%20from%20its%20Western%20counterpart%2C%20which%20was%20demonstratively%20partisan%20towards%20Israel.%20A%20majority%20of%20TV%20channels%20and%20newspapers%20actively%20decontextualised%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20and%20also%20failed%20to%20see%20and%20point%20out%20the%20visible%20disproportionality%20in%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98response%E2%80%99.%20The%20killing%20of%20Israeli%20children%20and%20women%20outraged%20them.%20But%20the%20killing%20of%20Gazan%20babies%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20bombing%20was%20because%20of%20Hamas%20embedding%20themselves%20within%20the%20civilian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20civilians%20was%20justified%20by%20suggesting%20that%20without%20their%20support%2C%20Hamas%20would%20not%20thrive.%20If%20they%20were%20not%20revolting%20against%20Hamas%2C%20they%20were%20complicit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Western%20media%20and%20political%20leadership%20kept%20calling%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20%E2%80%98unprovoked%E2%80%99%2C%20totally%20neglecting%20the%20underlying%20context%20%E2%80%93%20which%20includes%20the%20daily%20violence%20against%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20not%20only%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20but%20also%20by%20settlers%20who%20are%20given%20arms%20and%20cover%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2019-03-12%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fhow-palestinian-land-goes-from-the-army-to-the-settlers%2F0000017f-e3ae-d804-ad7f-f3fe6a2f0000%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20state%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F7%2F8%2Fhow-israel-backs-settlers-to-confiscate-palestinian-lands%5C%22%3Eloot%20and%20steal%20Palestinian%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20houses%20and%20even%20kill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20out%20this%20dishonesty%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.democracynow.org%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2Famira_hass_on_gaza_humanitarian_crisis%5C%22%3EAmira%20Hass%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veteran%20Israe