Israel%20at%20this%20difficult%20hour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20big%20media%20tried%20to%20portray%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fstand-in-solidarity-with-israel-at-this-difficult-hour-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F104241034.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-reiterates-solidarity-phone-call-netanyahu-israel-hamas%5C%22%3EModi%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20entry%20into%20the%20war%20against%20%E2%80%98terror%E2%80%99%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20it%2C%20has%20driven%20fear%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20noted%20that%20India%20had%20associated%20its%20reputation%20with%20Israel%20and%20forsaken%20its%20role%20as%20a%20voice%20of%20moderation%2C%20which%20it%20has%20performed%20historically%20since%20independence.%20While%20expressing%20shock%20at%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20India%20could%20have%20asked%20for%20restraint%2C%20by%20calling%20upon%20Israel%20not%20to%20target%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza.%20Only%20five%20days%20later%2C%20it%20tried%20to%20correct%20its%20official%20position%20when%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fworld%2Fstory%2Findia-supports-establishment-of-independent-state-of-palestine-mea-401804-2023-10-12%5C%22%3Ereiterated%20its%20stand%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20sovereign%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20after%2018%20days%20of%20the%20Israeli%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%2C%20India%20has%20not%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20It%20has%20not%20called%20upon%20the%20international%20community%20to%20mediate.%20That%20indicates%20that%20it%20is%20allowing%20Israel%20to%20continue%20its%20genocidal%20attack%20on%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-war-on-palestinians-language-in-the-service-of-the-unspeakable%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20War%20on%20Palestinians%3A%20Language%20in%20the%20Service%20of%20the%20Unspeakable%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20election%20agenda%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20journalist%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20told%20me%20he%20is%20worried%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Israeli%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20state%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20next%20month.%20His%20worry%20is%20not%20misplaced.%20If%20you%20follow%20the%20big%20media%2C%20which%20acts%20like%20a%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20you%20can%20see%20that%20the%20trope%20of%20terror%20is%20being%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-pro-bjp-whatsapp-facebook-groups-are-using-the-israel-hamas-war-to-stoke-islamophobia%5C%22%3Evilify%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20suggested%20that%20Islamic%20countries%20should%20accommodate%20Palestinians%20and%20make%20Gaza%20available%20to%20Israel.%20This%20is%20what%20they%20have%20been%20wishing%20for%20Indian%20Muslims%3A%20to%20be%20packed%20off%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20hard%20to%20ascertain%20that%20the%20conflict%20in%20West%20Asia%20would%20be%20used%20%E2%80%93%20is%20already%20being%20used%20%E2%80%93%20to%20demonise%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20propaganda%20cell%20is%20working%20overtime%20to%20tell%20its%20constituents%20that%20Palestinian%20%E2%80%98terror%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20result%20of%20the%20policies%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20or%20the%20Congress%20party.%20The%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-terrorist-attack-p-chidambaram-congress-resolution-palestine-cause-2448241-2023-10-13%5C%22%3Estand%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20different%20from%20Modi%E2%80%99s.%20It%20did%20condemn%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20but%20immediately%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CWC%20calls%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20for%20negotiations%20to%20begin%20on%20all%20outstanding%20issues%20including%20the%20imperative%20issues%20that%20have%20given%20rise%20to%20the%20present%20conflict.%E2%80%9D%20It%20did%20not%20take%20time%20to%20ask%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20be%20respected%20and%20spoke%20for%20their%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAssam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20compared%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20with%20that%20of%20Pakistan.%20He%20taunted%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20who%20had%20talked%20about%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20over%20their%20land%20and%20resources%20and%20said%20that%20all%20Indian%20prime%20ministers%20had%20stood%20firmly%20with%20Palestine%2C%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-india-position-israel-palestine-conflict-himanta-sarma-says-think-ncp-chief-will-send-supriya-sule-to-gaza-to-fight-for-hamas-4494154%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dfight%2520for%2520Hamas.-%2C%2522I%2520think%2520Sharad%2520Pawar%2520will%2520send%2520Supriya%2520(Sule)%2520to%2Con%2520the%2520Israel%252DPalestine%2520issue.%5C%22%3Easking%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pawar%20to%20send%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%20to%20fight%20for%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20BJP%20leader%2C%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CPawar%20ji%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20same%20government%20that%20shed%20tears%20on%20the%20Batla%20House%20encounter%20and%20slept%20while%20there%20were%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20soil%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20very%20disturbing%20when%20a%20senior%20leader%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPawarSpeaks%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40PawarSpeaks%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20makes%20preposterous%20statements%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20a%20terror%20attack%20in%20Israel.%20The%20menace%20of%20terrorism%20has%20to%20be%20condemned%20in%20all%20forms%2C%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20a%20pity%20that%20a%20person%20who%20has%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20Defence%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Piyush%20Goyal%20(%40PiyushGoyal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPiyushGoyal%2Fstatus%2F1714613554110754820%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupport%20for%20Palestine%20is%20being%20treated%20as%20support%20for%20terrorism.%20You%20can%20be%20booked%20or%20jailed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F25%2Fpro-israel-rallies-allowed-in-india-but-palestine-solidarity-sees-crackdown%5C%22%3Esupporting%20Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20Protests%20are%20not%20allowed%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20India%20is%20in%20consonance%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20anti-Muslim%2C%20anti-minority%20politics%20represented%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20idea%20of%20Israel%20as%20a%20country%20in%20which%20Jews%20are%20first-class%20citizens%20and%20others%20second%20is%20attractive%20to%20the%20BJP%20supporters%2C%20who%20want%20Hindus%20to%20be%20treated%20similarly%20in%20India.%20They%20want%20India%20to%20become%20a%20majoritarian%20democracy%20like%20Israel.%20They%20also%20share%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Israeli%20Jews%20who%20consider%20Palestinians%20as%20lesser%20humans%20who%20are%20unlike%20them%20in%20all%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOutsiders%20are%20puzzled%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2022%2F12%2Findias-hindutva-proponents-and-zionist-israel-strange-bedfellows%2F%5C%22%3Esupport%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20or%20its%20parent%20body%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20for%20Israel.%20Did%20it%20not%20endorse%20the%20notion%20of%20the%20Nazi%20%E2%80%98Final%20Solution%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20Jewish%20question%3F%20How%20can%20it%20now%20justify%20its%20support%20for%20Jews%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20paradox%20can%20be%20explained%20by%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20belief%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20dominance.%20They%20admire%20those%20who%20dominate%20and%20use%20violence%20to%20maintain%20their%20dominance%20over%20others.%20A%20hundred%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Nazis%20were%20the%20dominant%20power.%20Now%20it%20is%20Israel.%20The%20RSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fhistory%2Frss-golwalkar-links-nazism%5C%22%3Eworshipped%20Hitler%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%2C%20now%20it%20is%20a%20disciple%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-israel-palestine-war-is-a-stain-on-every-one-of-us%5C%22%3EThe%20Israel-Palestine%20War%20Is%20a%20Stain%20on%20Every%20One%20of%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20journalist%20friend%20was%20also%20perturbed%20by%20the%20silence%20on%20campuses.%20Why%20is%20our%20youth%20not%20speaking%20out%3F%20There%20are%20many%20reasons.%20But%20one%20reason%20is%20that%20they%20are%20not%20adequately%20informed.%20They%20depend%20on%20TV%20Big%20Media%20and%20WhatsApp%20for%20inforamation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20even%20the%20nearly%20six-month-long%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20stir%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%20There%20are%20hardly%20any%20public%20protests%20demanding%20peace%20there.%20It%20is%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20think%20about%20Palestine.%20For%20them%2C%20there%20is%20an%20entity%20called%20Israel%20which%20is%20being%20threatened%20by%20terrorists%20led%20by%20Hamas.%20Palestine%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20exist%20in%20their%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20people%20who%20invoke%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%20to%20speak%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinians.%20But%20a%20significant%20section%20of%20Hindus%20now%20believe%20that%20India%20has%20to%20correct%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwrongs%E2%80%9D%20committed%20by%20those%20great%20leaders.%20Israel%20is%20cited%20as%20an%20ideal%20in%20these%20circles.%20Its%20violent%20methods%20to%20control%20people%20perhaps%20appeal%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20there%20is%20no%20parallel%20education%20about%20liberation%20struggles%20in%20India.%20Given%20the%20shift%20in%20demographics%2C%20with%20NFHS-5%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fhalf-indias-population-under-age-30-nfhs-explained-7910458%2F%5C%22%3Erevealing%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2052%25%20of%20Indians%20are%20under%20the%20age%20of%2030%2C%20present-day%20Indians%20do%20not%20have%20a%20memory%20of%20apartheid%20South%20Africa%20and%20know%20little%20of%20the%20stellar%20role%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20leadership%20took%20in%20mobilising%20international%20opinion%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20that%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20accept%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20Indians%20are%20not%20averse%20to%20some%20kind%20of%20apartheid%20as%20they%20themselves%20believe%20in%20a%20caste-segregated%20society%2C%20with%20entrenched%20notions%20of%20hierarchy%20and%20dominance.%20Israel%20has%20achieved%20this.%20It%20may%2C%20therefore%2C%20be%20a%20reflex%20to%20admire%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698240954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25174409%2Fimage-1432.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-india-forsakerole-voice-of-moderation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20increasing%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20the%20country%20is%20in%20consonance%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20anti-Muslim%2C%20anti-minority%20politics%20represented%20by%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-palestine-c