3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Chhattisgarh%20Congress%20chief%20Deepak%20Baij%20has%20defended%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20not%20give%20tickets%20to%2022%20sitting%20MLAs%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20next%20month%20and%20said%20that%20while%20there%20was%20some%20%E2%80%9Cresentment%E2%80%9D%2C%20none%20of%20these%20legislators%20will%20be%20leaving%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20(October%2022)%2C%20the%20Congress%20released%20its%20third%20and%20final%20list%20of%20seven%20candidates.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20party%20had%20released%20two%20separate%20lists%20with%2030%20and%2053%20candidates%20each.%20Chhattisgarh%20will%20vote%20in%20two%20phases%2C%20on%20November%207%20and%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EBaij%2C%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Bastar%20who%20is%20contesting%20the%20state%20elections%20from%20Chitrakoot%20constituency%20this%20time%2C%20said%20that%20the%20party%20had%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20%E2%80%9Cwinning%20candidates%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20We%20have%20said%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20that%20since%20a%20government%20has%20to%20be%20formed%20again%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20we%20will%20only%20give%20tickets%20to%20winning%20candidates.%20The%20high%20command%20and%20the%20party%20have%20taken%20this%20historic%20decision.%20We%20are%20all%20fighting%20together%20and%20we%20will%20form%20the%20government%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20differences%20within%20the%20party%20on%20account%20of%20the%20sitting%20MLAs%20being%20denied%20tickets%2C%20Baij%20said%20that%20discussions%20were%20held%20with%20those%20who%20were%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20some%20resentment%20%5Bamong%20the%20members%5D%20and%20that%20is%20natural.%20If%20someone%E2%80%99s%20ticket%20is%20cut%2C%20then%20they%20will%20feel%20upset%20and%20some%20resentment.%20But%20we%20have%20had%20discussions%20with%20everyone%20and%20spoken%20with%20them%20and%20no%20one%20will%20leave%20the%20party%20and%20everyone%20will%20help%20the%20party%20win%20the%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20looking%20to%20retain%20power%20in%20the%20state%20after%20it%20trounced%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%202018%20elections.%20The%20saffron%20party%20had%20been%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20since%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%2068%20of%20the%2090%20seats%20in%20the%202018%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%20said%20that%20the%20party%20is%20looking%20to%20repeat%20such%20a%20performance%20by%20highlighting%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20objective%20is%20to%20highlight%20farmers%E2%80%99%20issues%2C%20youth%20issues%2C%20and%20the%20welfare%20of%20women%20and%20children%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20along%20with%20education%20and%20health.%20In%20these%20sectors%2C%20our%20government%20has%20done%20good%20work%20and%20these%20are%20the%20issues%20that%20we%20will%20take%20to%20the%20people.%20We%20will%20also%20highlight%20the%20good%20work%20that%20we%20plan%20to%20do%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30141532%2Fimage-1094.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30141532%2Fimage-1094.png%20688w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30141532%2Fimage-1094-300x163.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%