rg%20MP%20Vijay%20Baghel%20has%20been%20fielded%20to%20take%20on%20his%20uncle%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20in%20the%20Patan%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhupesh%20Baghel%20is%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20area.%20His%20candidature%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20bid%20to%20woo%20voters%20from%20OBC%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20give%20us%20a%20direct%20fight%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20conduct%20a%20caste%20survey%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20and%20this%20will%20benefit%20those%20whose%20numbers%20are%20more%20but%20are%20not%20able%20to%20access%20the%20fruits%20of%20development.%20The%20chief%20minister%20is%20fighting%20from%20Patan%20and%20he%20will%20win%20with%20a%20record%20number%20of%20votes.%20There%20is%20no%20challenge%20and%20Vijay%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20will%20not%20make%20any%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Union%20government%20taking%20credit%20for%20our%20good%20work%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%2C%20the%20Bastar%20MP%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20reducing%20Maoist%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20claim%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-will-be-free-of-naxalism-if-bjp-comes-to-power-amit-shah-4496186%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bastar%E2%80%99s%20Jagdalpur%20last%20week%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIn%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20incidents%20of%20(Naxal)%20violence%20declined%20by%2052%25%2C%20deaths%20(in%20Maoist%20violence)%20came%20down%20by%2070%25%2C%20civilian%20deaths%20decreased%20by%2068%25%2C%20while%20the%20(number%20of)%20Naxal-affected%20districts%20declined%20by%2062%25.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%20said%20that%20peace%20in%20the%20Maoist-affected%20regions%20is%20due%20to%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20good%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government.%20These%20are%20double%20standards%20in%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20this%20won%E2%80%99t%20work.%20Amit%20Shah%20says%20something%2C%20%5BBJP%20president%20J.P.%5D%20Nadda%20says%20something%20else.%20Different%20leaders%20are%20saying%20different%20things%20and%20they%20are%20not%20on%20the%20same%20page%20on%20this%20%5Bmatter%5D%20either.%20But%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20has%20done%20good%20work%20and%20there%20is%20peace%20in%20Bastar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Nadda%20had%20said%20that%20Naxal%20activities%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fnaxal-incidents-have-increased-in-chhattisgarh-under-congress-rule-says-bjp-president-j-p-nadda%2Famp_articleshow%2F97826342.cms%5C%22%3Eincreased%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20under%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20independent%20India%2C%20residents%20of%20more%20than%20120%20villages%20in%20Bastar%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Fchhattisgarh%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-residents-of-over-120-villages-in-maoist-hit-bastar-to-vote-in-their-own-villages-for-first-time-since-independence-2725287%5C%22%3Evote%20in%20their%20own%20settlements%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20Polling%20stations%20will%20be%20set%20up%20in%20these%20places%2C%20which%20were%20earlier%20Maoist%20strongholds%2C%20and%20voters%20had%20to%20earlier%20trek%208-10%20kilometres%20to%20cast%20their%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaij%20said%20that%20this%20development%20was%20made%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Congress%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20government%20has%20worked%20to%20develop%20those%20interior%20villages%20where%20rations%20would%20not%20reach%2C%20where%20there%20was%20no%20electricity%2C%20water%2C%20roads%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20schools.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20is%20peace%20in%20these%20areas%20now.%20They%20will%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20Adivasis%2C%20our%20government%20has%20worked%20very%20well%20and%20we%20will%20plan%20better%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20In%20these%20interior%20villages%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20open%20ration%20shops%2C%20did%20not%20help%20people%20with%20receiving%20their%20Aadhaar%20cards%2C%20and%20did%20not%20provide%20electricity%2C%20health%2C%20and%20education.%20Our%20government%20has%20delivered%20%3Cem%3Evikas%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Bprogress%5D.%20We%20have%20opened%20ration%20shops.%20There%20were%20none.%20We%20have%20made%20Aadhaar%20cards%20for%20people.%20We%20have%20built%20schools%20and%20hospitals.%20If%20the%20BJP%20thinks%20they%20have%20constructed%20a%20building%20on%20the%20roads%20initially%20built%20by%20us%20and%20calling%20it%20%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20then%20good%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20these%20villages%2C%20Baij%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Ctight%20security%E2%80%9D%20measures%20have%20been%20implemented%20and%20camps%20have%20been%20set%20up%20to%20ensure%20a%20peaceful%20polling%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698238855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25182130%2FF8-AIk5bsAAg7Ie.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-chhattisgarh-party-chief-deepak-baij-interview-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deepak%20Baij%20has%20defended%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20not%20give