%20of%20the%20satellite.%20However%2C%20TJ%20Kouri%2C%20the%20head%20of%20space%20object%20visualization%20firm%20DigitalArsenal.io%2C%20believes%20Luch-5X%2FOlymp-K-2%20is%20stationed%20near%20the%20Eutelsat%203B%20satellite%2C%20a%20commercial%20communications%20satellite%20built%20by%20Airbus%20in%20France%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D938a6ff11f3c53f65e898d45836f1e8c94a70ac5bb1962ed7ddfc7b18e1f3eef%26postID%3D6538db17cf767c5e2eb31097%26postSlug%3Drussia-satellite-luch-olymp-moved-close-eutelsat-report-spy-defense-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fposts%252Ftj-k-5754554_ssa-space-luch-activity-7120187196405395456-d2X7%252F%253Futm_source%253Dshare%2526utm_medium%253Dmember_ios%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEutelsat's%203B%20satellite%20provides%20broadband%2C%20data%2C%20telecom%2C%20and%20video%20services%20across%20Europe%2C%20Africa%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Central%20Asia%2C%20and%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuch-5-X%2FOlymp-K-2%20also%20recently%20lingered%20near%20Eutelsat's%209B%20satellite%2C%20which%20provides%20satellite%20coverage%20across%20Europe%20for%20TV%20channels%2C%20per%20Kouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you're%20seeing%20is%20behavior%20that%20could%20be%20considered%20unfriendly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schaffer%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20director%20of%20space%20policy%20at%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20per%20Breaking%20Defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuch-5-X%2FOlymp%20K-2%20isn't%20close%20enough%20to%20crash%20into%20the%20unnamed%20commercial%20satellite.%20The%20distance%20at%20which%20it%20is%20parked%20wouldn't%20trigger%20the%20collision%20detectors%20aboard%20the%20non-Russian%20satellite%2C%20Breaking%20Defense%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20main%20concern%20is%20that%20it%20might%20be%20spying%20on%20sensitive%20intelligence%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20it's%20not%20close%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20safety%20threat%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20doesn't%20potentially%20present%20a%20security%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20Schaffer%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspacenews.com%2Fslingshot-aerospace-harnessing-ai-to-track-suspicious-satellites%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espacenews.com.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20a%20commercial%20communication%20satellite%20company%20you%20may%20not%20want%20a%20Russian%20spy%20satellite%20listening%20in%20on%20your%20communications%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20per%20spacenews.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20behavior%20is%20not%20altogether%20unexpected.%20Analysts%20said%20it%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20another%20Luch%20Olymp%20Russian%20spacecraft%20that%20caused%20a%20stir%20in%202015%20after%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-what-putin-was-likely-doing-as-a-kgb-spy-in-germany-2015-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20it%20approached%20commercial%20intelligence%20satellites%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20US%20firm%20Intelsat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20%26quot%3Bwell-known%20GEO%20%5Bgeostationary%20Earth%20Orbit%5D%20inspector%20satellite%26quot%3B%20also%20caused%20concern%20as%20it%20loitered%20near%20Intelsat%20satellites%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcsis-website-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fs3fs-public%2F2023-04%2F230414_Bingen_Space_Assessment.pdf%3FVersionId%3DoMsUS8MupLbZi3BISPrqPCKd5jDejZnJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20security%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20US%20think%20tank%20the%20Council%20for%20Strategic%20International%20Studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Luch%20Olymp%20K-2's%20payload%20is%20poorly%20understood%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20likely%20packs%20more%20advanced%20signals%20intelligence%20capabilities%20and%20operational%20techniques%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Clont%2C%20director%20of%20Space%20Dom