ice%2Fpuppy-dog-passenger-removed-southwest-flight-b2434326.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ethe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20video%20has%20been%20watched%20more%20than%201.4%20million%20times%20as%20of%20publish%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caption%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20puppy%20was%20whining%20a%20little%20and%20the%20flight%20attendant%20boarding%20everyone%20walked%20up%20to%20her%20and%20said%2C%20if%20your%20dogs%20don't%20be%20quiet%2C%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20fly%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Price%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20was%20on%20our%20flight%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSouthwestAir%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40SouthwestAir%3C%2Fa%3E%20yesterday.%20She%20was%20literally%20petty%20her%20new%20puppy%20through%20the%20mesh%20of%20the%20completely%20zipped%20carrier%2C%20and%20they%20booted%20her%20off.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHeuMR4jzJ4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHeuMR4jzJ4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Sara%20(%40_Sara_Price_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F_Sara_Price_%2Fstatus%2F1715745590494310850%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUpon%20boarding%2C%20the%20dog%20owner%2C%20who%20happened%20to%20be%20seated%20in%20the%20same%20row%20as%20Ms%20Price%2C%20placed%20the%20carrier%20on%20her%20lap%20and%20proceeded%20to%20caress%20her%20dog.%20According%20to%20Ms%20Price's%20account%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20then%20came%20over%20to%20the%20dog%20owner%20and%20requested%20that%20she%20zip%20up%20the%20carrier%20and%20store%20it%20beneath%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Southwest's%20pet%20policy%2C%20%26quot%3BPets%20must%20be%20secured%20in%20the%20pet%20carrier%20at%20all%20times%20while%20in%20the