ugust%2017%2C%202021.%20The%20women%20in%20this%20story%20are%20not%20pictured.%3Cp%3EMenahem%20Kahana%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFemale%20soldiers%20with%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20fought%20back%20Hamas%20militants%20on%20October%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20soldiers%20killed%20around%20100%20Hamas%20militants%2C%20their%20commander%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fdefense-news%2Farticle-769134%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Jerusalem%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20commander%20said%20the%20soldiers%C2%A0%26quot%3Bemerged%C2%A0as%C2%A0heroes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Israeli%20commander%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fdefense-news%2Farticle-769134%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Jerusalem%20Post%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20her%20battalion%2C%20made%20up%20of%20mostly%20female%20soldiers%2C%20killed%20around%20100%20Hamas%20militants%20during%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Caracal%20commander%20Lt.-Col.%20Or%20Ben-Yehuda%20told%20the%20outlet%20the%20women%20%26quot%3Bemerged%20as%20heroes%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20actions%20near%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20October%207%2C%20Ben-Yehuda%20said%20she%20received%20a%20message%20reporting%20an%20infiltration%20of%20heavily%20armed%20militants%20near%20the%20kibbutzim%20of%20Sufa%20and%20Nirim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20yet%20knowing%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20attacks%2C%20she%20told%20her%20soldiers%3A%20%26quot%3BStay%20alert.%20We%20might%20cross%20paths.%20We%20are%20a%20strong%20squad%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20arrival%20in%20the%20Sufa%20kibbutz%2C%20Ben-Yehuda%20said%20she%20saw%20how%20big%20the%20Hamas%20infiltration%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20out%20to%20eliminate%20terrorists.%20Infiltration%20into%20Israel%20is%20happening%2C%20and%20it's%20spreading%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20her%20battalion%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Jerusalem%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombat%20between%20the%20battalion%20and%20the%20militants%20lasted%20nearly%20four%20hours%2C%20she%20said.%20It%20took%20the%20Caracal%20battalion%20about%2014%20hours%20to%20secure%20the%20base%20alongside%20other%20units%2C%20the%20outlet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Caracal%20Battalion%2C%20which%20is%20tasked%20with%20protecting%20Israel's%20border%2C%20is%20one%20of%20three%20mixed-gender%20combat%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20established%20in%202004%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20incorporating%20women%20in%20service%20into%20combat%20units.%20Two-thirds%20of%20its%20members%20are%20women%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idf.il%2Fen%2Fmini-sites%2Fground-forces%2Fborder-defense%2Fcaracal%2Fcaracal-battalion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF).%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20her%20squad%20members%20were%20killed%2C%20though%20Ben-Yehuda%20herself%20came%20very%20close%20to%20being%20shot%20at%20point-blank%20range%2C%20she%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20training%20and%20performance%20on%20the%20battlefield%20have%20erased%20any%20doubts.%20They%20fought%20bravely%2C%20saved%20lives%2C%20and%20emerged%20as%20heroes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20Jerusalem%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20more%20doubts%20about%20female%20combat%20soldiers%2C%20who%20have%20triumphed%20in%20every%20encounter%20with%20terrorists%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen-Yehuda%20added%20that%20her%20battalion%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bpreparing%20for%20any%20potential%20ground%20maneuvers%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20border%20area%20and%20the%20Egyptian%20border.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20one%20of%20only%20a%20few%20countries%20where%20military%20service%20is%20compulsory%20for%20women.%20In%20the%20IDF%2C%20they%20serve%20a%20variety%20of%20roles%2C%20including%20in%20elite%20search%20and%20rescue%20and%20combat%20engineering%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-declares-state-of-war-hamas-launches-massive-surprise-attack-2023-10%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDuring%20its%20surprise%20terrorist%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hamas%20militants%20took%20more%20than%20200%20people%20hostage%20and%20left%20more%20than%201%2C300%20Israelis%20and%20foreign%20nationals%20dead%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20since%20responded%20with%20relentless%20airstrikes%20on%20Gaza%2C%20which%20Palestinian%20officials%20say%20have%20killed%20at%20least%205%2C000%20people%20at%20the%20time%20of%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-commander-says-unit-mostly-women-killed-100-hamas-militants-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698237328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538e4b8356802a56be31ea4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-commander-says-unit-mostly-women-killed-100-hamas-militants-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Female%20IDF%20soldiers%20were%20among%20the%20troops%20who%20fought%20off%20a%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20October%207.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sankel%40businessinsider.com%20(Sophia%20Ankel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-commander-says-unit-mostly-women-killed-100-hamas-militants-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vijay's%20Leo%20vs%20SRK's%20Jawan%3B%