%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104697695.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFrom%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20calling%20Karan%20Johar%20the%20flagbearer%20of%20nepotism%20to%20Salman%20Khan%20declaring%20that%20he%20is%20a%20virgin%2C%20here's%20a%20list%20of%20some%20of%20the%20most%20controversial%20celebrity%20statements%20made%20on%20Koffee%20With%20Karan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fnepotism-to-virginity-most-controversial-celeb-statements-on-koffee-with-karan%2Fphotostory%2F104697695.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Leaves%20Behind%20a%20Vast%20Legacy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25174513%2FF9IKL-eaYAAF6Mi.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20enigma%20wrapped%20in%20a%20mystery%E2%80%9D%20sums%20up%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20%E2%80%93%20the%20man%2C%20the%20cricketer%20and%20his%20persona.%20The%20legacy%20of%20the%20famous%20spinner%20is%20vast%3B%20the%20spectrum%20of%20his%20personality%20and%20cricketing%20feats%20would%20need%20a%20few%20kilobytes%20of%20computer%20space%20to%20explain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBish%20or%20skip%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20how%20I%20fondly%20addressed%20him%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20larger-than-life%20character%3B%20outspoken%2C%20hilarious%2C%20honest%2C%20he%20said%20things%20which%20would%20create%20a%20controversy.%20%E2%80%9CCompromise%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20he%20would%20often%20berate%20it%20as%20a%20weak%20word!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%201972%20that%20I%20first%20met%20Bish.%20He%20had%20already%20%E2%80%98spun%E2%80%99%20India%20to%20victory%20in%20England%20under%20Ajit%20Wadekar%20and%20was%20a%20big%20name.%20I%20had%20made%20my%20debut%20for%20Delhi%20a%20year%20earlier%20in%201971.%20Gulshan%20Rai%20Kashyap%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20Delhi%20Ranji%20Trophy%20player%20who%20was%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Ranji%20side%20and%20was%20also%20the%20manager%20of%20North%20Zone%20universities%20for%20the%20Vizzy%20Trophy%2C%20where%20I%20had%20a%20successful%20run%20in%201971%20%E2%80%93%20literally%20held%20my%20hand%20and%20took%20me%20to%20meet%20Bish.%20There%20started%20a%20long%20friendship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22qme%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FNewProfilePic%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23NewProfilePic%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ff3r6lpWerd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ff3r6lpWerd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANGAD%20BEDI%20(%40Imangadbedi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FImangadbedi%2Fstatus%2F1717004344896471120%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Indian%20cricket%20circles%2C%20the%20great%20spinner%20was%20always%20referred%20to%20as%20%3Cem%3EPaaji%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20the%20Punjabi%20word%20for%20elder%20brother%20%E2%80%93%20while%20internationally%20he%20was%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9CBishan%E2%80%9D%20or%20just%20%E2%80%9CBedi%E2%80%9D.%20For%20me%2C%20his%20junior%20by%20some%20five%20years%2C%20he%20was%20always%20%E2%80%98Bish%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20and%20he%20never%20minded%20it%20or%20made%20an%20issue%20of%20me%20not%20referring%20to%20him%20as%20Paaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20century%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20has%20seen%20many%20great%20personalities%20adorn%20the%20game%2C%20famous%20names%20stretching%20from%20Ranjitsinhji%2C%20Duleepsinhji%2C%20Tiger%20Pataudi%2C%20Kapil%20Dev%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20M.S.%20Dhoni%20and%20Virat%20Kohli.%20Yet%2C%20Bish%20was%20in%20a%20class%20of%20his%20own.%20His%20garrulous%20laugh%2C%20warm%20hug%2C%20colourful%20turbans%2C%20%3Cem%3Epatkas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20no-nonsense%20attitude%20typified%20him%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field.%20A%20man%20of%20strong%20faith%20and%20belief%2C%20Bish%20often%20went%20out%20of%20his%20way%20to%20make%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECricket%2C%20to%20Bish%2C%20was%20not%20just%20a%20game%20of%20bat%20and%20ball.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20old%20adage%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20battle%20of%20Waterloo%20was%20won%20on%20the%20fields%20of%20Eton%20and%20Harrow%E2%80%9D%20was%20a%20yardstick%20to%20judge%20one%E2%80%99s%20actions%20and%20life.%20He%20was%20a%20strong-willed%20character%20and%20had%20seen%20the%20ups%20and%20downs%20of%20life%20at%20close%20quarters.%20What%20stood%20out%20over%20the%20years%20were%20his%20commitment%2C%20dedication%2C%20honesty%20and%20uprightness.%20These%20days%2C%20all%20such%20traits%20are%20not%20usually%20found%20in%20one%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBish%20was%20born%20in%20Amritsar%20and%20completed%20his%20education%20there.%20He%20initially%20joined%20Khalsa%20College%20for%20his%20graduation%20but%20shifted%20a%20year%20later%20to%20Hindu%20College%20in%20the%20same%20city.%20It%20was%20at%20the%20latter%20that%20he%20met%20a%20cricket%20coach%20of%20great%20calibre%2C%20Gyan%20Prakash.%20Bish%20and%20Gyan%20developed%20a%20close%20relationship.%20The%20mentor%20found%20a%20dedicated%20pupil%20as%20Gyan%20Prakash%20drilled%20many%20lessons%20and%20taught%20the%20ways%20of%20the%20world%20to%20his%20pupil%2C%20besides%20the%20nuances%20of%20spin%2C%20the%20dip%20in%20flight%2C%20the%20craft%20of%20making%20the%20ball%20%E2%80%98talk%E2%80%99%20and%20of%20course%20the%20balance.%20Bish%20initially%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20fast%20bowler%20but%20was%20dissuaded%20by%20Gurpal%20Singh%2C%20a%20first-class%20cricketer%2C%20and%20later%20by%20Gyan%20Prakash%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20spinner%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20later%2C%20Bish%20narrated%20an%20incident%20from%20his%20early%20days%20at%20home%20in%20Amritsar%20which%20showed%20his%20strong-headed%20nature.%20His%20father%20had%20an%20argument%20with%20the%20young%20Bish%20which%20became%20a%20bit%20heated.%20Bish%20recollected%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20upset%20that%20I%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20him%20for%20the%20next%20six%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOften%20words%20like%20%E2%80%98obdurate%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98dictatorial%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98stubborn%E2%80%99%20were%20used%20to%20describe%20Bish.%20But%20even%20his%20detractors%20acknowledge%20that%20he%20had%20a%20warm%20heart%2C%20a%20spontaneous%20bellow%20and%20loud%20laughter.%20Yes%2C%20he%20would%20stand%20up%20for%20his%20rights%20always%2C%20often%20calling%20a%20spade%20a%20bloody%20shovel.%20If%20only%20his%20early%20mentors%20had%20tutored%20him%20on%20the%20virtues%20of%20diplomacy%2C%20where%20would%20that%20have%20taken%20him%3F%20As%20former%20England%20captain%20Mike%20Brearley%20stressed%2C%20%E2%80%9CBishan%20was%20no%20diplomat.%20He%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20man%20unafraid%20to%20speak%20his%20mind%20even%20if%20it%20bordered%20on%20the%20intemperate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-bowled-to-deceive-but-frank-and-big-hearted-was-the-least-deceptive-of-men%5C%22%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Bowled%20to%20Deceive%20but%2C%20Frank%20and%20Big-Hearted%2C%20Was%20the%20Least%20Deceptive%20of%20Men%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20cricketing%20front%2C%20Bish%20was%20appointed%20as%20captain%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Ranji%20team%20in%201973.%20The%20team%20was%20struggling%20and%20the%20old%20warhorses%20were%20a%20spent%20force.%20Many%20years%20after%20he%20retired%2C%20Bish%20recollected%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20not%20too%20enamoured%20by%20the%20prospects%20of%20leading%20the%20team%2C%20and%20in%20fact%20declined%20the%20offer.%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0The%20Delhi%20state%20cricket%20association%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98fiefdom%E2%80%99%20of%20a%20strong-willed%20administrator%2C%20and%20Bish%20felt%20the%20gentleman%20and%20he%20would%20end%20up%20in%20arguments%20and%20there%20would%20be%20interference%20at%20all%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBish%2C%20was%20a%20star%20by%20that%20time.%20He%20laid%20down%20his%20terms%20before%20accepting%20the%20responsibility%20of%20captaining%20the%20Delhi%20Ranji%20team%20%E2%80%93%20he%20would%20do%20so%20only%20if%20he%20was%20given%20a%20free%20hand%20and%20total%20control.%20Thus%20began%20a%20long%20journey%20during%20which%20Bish%20would%20ensure%20that%20players%20from%20Delhi%20and%20North%20Zone%2C%20till%20then%20the%20whipping%20boys%20of%20Indian%20Cricket%2C%20climbed%20to%20the%20top%20and%20won%20every%20trophy%20in%20Indian%20cricket.%20Bish%20coached%20the%20Punjab%20side%20to%20their%20maiden%20Ranji%20Trophy%20title%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBish%20was%20the%20best%20left-arm%20bowler%20in%20India%20and%20there%20was%20no%20one%20close%20to%20him.%20His%20action%20was%20described%20as%20poetry%20in%20motion%2C%20and%20Jim%20Laker%20famously%20described%20his%20idea%20of%20euphoria%20as%20watching%20a%20match%20at%20Lord%E2%80%99s%20with%20Ray%20Lindwall%20bowling%20from%20one%20end%20and%20Bishan%20Bedi%20from%20the%20other!%20There%20have%20been%20many%20equally%20colourful%20analogies.%20As%20a%20bowler%2C%20Bish%20was%20not%20afraid%20of%20batsmen%20hitting%20him%20for%20boundaries.%20When%20he%20applauded%20a%20six%2C%20often%20one%20wondered%20if%20it%20was%20genuine%20or%20if%20the%20great%20Sardar%20was%20playing%20on%20the%20batsman%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20Probably%20both.%20Bish%20enjoyed%20good%20cricket%2C%20even%20from%20the%20opposition.%20Maybe%20the%20applause%20was%20to%20incite%20the%20batsman%20to%20repeat%20the%20stroke%20%E2%80%93%20for%20that%20gave%20him%20an%20opportunity%20to%20get%20his%20wicket.%20Clever!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20frequently%20prodded%20him%20for%20details%20of%20his%20cricketing%20battles%20with%20players%20like%20the%20Chappell%20brothers%20%E2%80%93%20Ian%20and%20Greg%3B%20Barry%20Richards%20and%20Geoff%20Boycott.%20It%20was%20fascinating%20to%20hear%20him%20reply.%20As%20Greg%20Chappell%20mentioned%2C%20%E2%80%9CBishan%20was%20a%20fierce%20competitor%20on%20the%20field%20and%20a%20thorough%20gentleman%20off%20it.%20My%20abiding%20memories%20are%20of%20a%20striking%20man%20in%20a%20blue%20turban%2C%20bowling%20with%20the%20most%20fluid%20action%20that%20I%20have%20ever%20witnessed%20and%20that%20he%20got%20me%20out%20regularly.%E2%80%9D%20Bish%20did%20not%20rely%20on%20extravagant%20spin.%20His%20full-bodied%20action%20allowed%20him%20to%20drift%20the%20ball%20and%20modify%20the%20pace%20subtly%20so%20that%20no%20two%20balls%20were%20the%20same.%20He%20also%20extracted%20considerable%20bounce%20with%20his%20high%20action%20and%20the%20overspin%20which%20he%20conjured%20with%20his%20magical%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20not%20an%20elegant%20mover%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20or%20in%20the%20field.%20In%20both%20departments%20he%20was%20clumsy.%20Like%20Colin%20Cowdrey%2C%20among%20batsmen%2C%20Bedi%20was%20one%20of%20those%20athletes%20whose%20athleticism%20was%20expressed%20almost%20exclusively%20in%20what%20he%20did%20best.%20A%20few%20easy%20steps%2C%20perfectly%20balanced%2C%20and%20he%20moved%20smoothly%20into%20the%20delivery%20stride.%20There%20was%20no%20sense%20of%20striving%2C%20no%20hiccups%2C%20just%20an%20easy%20flow.%20He%20bowled%20at%20the%20slower%20end%20of%20the%20spin%20bowler%E2%80%99s%20range%2C%20though%20not%20dead%20slow%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mike%20Brearley%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwisden.com%2Falmanack%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-the-most-beautiful-of-slow-bowlers-mike-brearley-almanack%5C%22%3Eaptly%20described%3C%2Fa%3E%20him.%20Brearley%20was%20enthralled%20by%20Bish%E2%80%99s%20guile%20and%20dexterity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETiger%20Pataudi%20mentioned%20to%20me%20that%20Bish%20was%20the%20only%20one%20who%20took%20coaching%20seriously%20and%20shared%20his%20love%20for%20the%20game%20with%20young%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi%20was%20a%20generous%20man.%20He%20had%20a%20rare%20blood%20group%20and%20once%20donated%20blood%20in%20Karachi%20in%20response%20to%20a%20newspaper%20appeal.%20Benazir%20Bhutto%20sent%20him%20two%20carpets%20and%20a%20tea%20set%2C%20while%20shopkeepers%20invited%20Bedi%20to%20help%20himself.%20This%20humanity%20was%20visible%20to%20all%20his%20teammates%2C%20as%20he%20would%20invite%20them%20over%20after%20a%20day%E2%80%99s%20play%20to%20enjoy%20a%20drink%20and%20a%20meal.%20He%20gave%20away%20expensive%20cricket%20gear%20to%20young%20cricketers.%20Challenge%20yourself%20to%20play%20better%2C%20he%20would%20tell%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBish%E2%80%99s%20love-hate%20relationship%20with%20cricket%20officialdom%20is%20well%20documented.%20Bish%20turned%20down%20so%20many%20%E2%80%98offers%E2%80%99.%20Kerry%20Packer%2C%20the%20Australian%20who%20started%20the%20rebel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWorld_Series_Cricket%5C%22%3EWorld%20Series%20Cricket%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201977%20made%20three%20attempts%20to%20lure%20him.%20Bish%20declined.%20BCCI%20asked%20Bish%20to%20join%20the%20IPL%20Governing%20Council%20and%20again%20the%20Sardar%20turned%20it%20down.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20sought%20his%20views%20on%20allowing%20persons%20beyond%20the%20age%20of%2070%20to%20serve%20as%20administrators%2C%20selectors%20and%20Bish%2C%20himself%20nearing%2070%2C%20said%20such%20officials%20and%20cricketers%20would%20be%20better%20off%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20guiding%20the%20next%20generation%20in%20administering%20the%20game.%20Each%20of%20the%20offers%20declined%20by%20Bish%20would%20have%20been%20hugely%20rewarding%20monetarily%2C%20but%20Bish%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20game%20needed%20to%20be%20better%20piloted.%20True%20wealth%20is%20a%20character%20that%20no%20one%20can%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOr%20probably%20he%20had%20learnt%20the%20art%20of%20being%20content%20as%20a%20child%2C%20when%20his%20mother%20used%20to%20take%20him%20to%20the%20Gurdwara%20to%20hear%20the%20Gurbani%20%E2%80%93%20recited%20at%20the%20Gurdwara%20from%20the%20Sikh%20Scripture%20Guru%20Granth%20Sahib.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EB.S.%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20fabled%20Indian%20spin%20quartet%2C%20aptly%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CBish%20loved%20to%20quote%20Sir%20Don%20Bradman%2C%20who%20when%20asked%20in%20a%20television%20interview%20what%20he%20would%20like%20to%20be%20remembered%20for%20had%20replied%3A%20integrity.%E2%80%9D%20That%20is%20something%20Bishan%20will%20always%20be%20remembered%20for%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20of%20Bish%E2%80%99s%20life%20were%20extremely%20painful%2C%20trying%20and%20indeed%20challenging.%20For%20an%20independent%2C%20physically%20active%20sportsman%20like%20Bish%20to%20be%20struck%20by%20ill-health%20was%20a%20huge%20challenge.%20When%20I%20met%20him%20in%202021%2C%20just%20before%20this%20period%20began%2C%20Bish%20had%20cooked%20a%20wonderful%20lunch.%20It%20was%20so%20exciting%20to%20swap%20tales%20and%20jokes%20as%20we%20savoured%20biryani%2C%20kebabs%20and%20a%20beer.%20Little%20did%20we%20know%20that%20in%20a%20few%20days%2C%20Bish%20would%20go%20under%20the%20knife.%20It%20laid%20him%20low%20but%20his%20fighting%20spirit%2C%20his%20never-say-die%20attitude%2C%20and%20the%20warmth%20and%20love%20of%20his%20family%20kept%20him%20in%20good%20cheer.%20Even%20at%20his%20lowest%2C%20he%20did%20not%20give%20up%20easily.%20He%20fondly%20mentioned%20that%20he%20enjoyed%20playing%20cricket%20with%20his%20granddaughter%20and%20praised%20her%20ability.%20A%20true%20family%20man%2C%20Bish%20was%20rightly%20proud%20of%20his%20son%2C%20Angad%2C%20and%20his%20acting%20career%20in%20Bollywood.%20He%20named%20the%20grandchildren%20and%20was%20always%20in%20a%20cheerful%20mood%20when%20he%20spoke%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FSardar-Spin-Celebration-Bishan-Singh%2Fdp%2F8195256643%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESardar%20of%20Spin%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20book%20edited%20by%20me%2C%20was%20released%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20September%202021%20to%20coincide%20with%20the%2075th%20birthday%20celebrations%20of%20the%20master%20spinner.%20Unable%2C%20due%20to%20a%20stroke%2C%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20he%20hugged%20me%20and%20had%20tears%20in%20his%20eyes.%20It%20was%20sad%20to%20see%20the%20Sardar%20of%20slow%20bowling%20weeping%2C%20but%20such%20are%20the%20undulations%20of%20life!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVenkat%20Sundaram%20is%20a%20former%20captain%20of%20the%20Delhi%20and%20North%20Zone%20cricket%20teams.%20He%20edited%20a%20book%20on%20Bedi%20titled%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Sardar%20of%20Spin%3Cem%3E.%20More%20recently%20he%20edited%20%3C%2Fem%3EIndian%20Cricket%20Then%20and%20Now%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698236955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25174513%2FF9IKL-eaYAAF6Mi.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-leaves-behind-a-vast-legacy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bish%20or%20skip%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20how%20I%20fondly%20addressed%20him%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20larger-than-life%20character%3B%20outspoken%2C%20hilarious%2C%20honest%2C%20he%20said%20things%20which%20would%20create%20a%20controversy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-leaves-behind-a-vast-legacy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft-backed%20AI%20safety%20forum%20names%20first%20director%2C%20plans%20advisory%20board%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698236776000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%