ile%20Investments%20and%20Fiasco%20Investments%20had%20purchased%20Reliance%20shares%20at%20one-fifth%20their%20market%20prices...His%20political%20connections%20had%20even%20given%20birth%20to%20a%20popular%20joke%20which%20divided%20the%20country's%20politicians%20in%20two%20groups%3A%20R-positive%20and%20R-negative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20lengthy%20excerpt%20is%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcompanies%2F40-years-ago-and-now-he-changed-the-idiom-of-doing-business-115011400005_1.html%5C%22%3Ecolumn%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20leading%20commentator%20Shyamal%20Majumdar%20on%20the%20legacy%20of%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Reliance%20Industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVP%20Singh%2C%20who%20became%20India's%20eighth%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20prominent%20'R-negative'%20politicians%20of%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaking%20Sides%20May%20Not%20Always%20Work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Finance%20Minister%20and%20later%2C%20the%20key%20challenger%20to%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20Congress%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%201989%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20VP%20Singh%20employed%20various%20tactics%20against%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani.%20He%20positioned%20himself%20as%20a%20corruption%20slayer%20who%20spared%20no%20one.%20It's%20widely%20known%20that%20his%20anti-Dhirubhai%20stance%20received%20generous%20support%20from%20a%20rival%20corporate%20lobby%20and%20certain%20sections%20of%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%201989%20election%20results%20didn't%20provide%20the%20resounding%20mandate%20that%20VP%20Singh%20and%20his%20supporters%20had%20hoped%20for.%20His%20Janata%20Dal%20managed%20only%20143%20of%20543%20seats%2C%20with%20a%20vote%20share%20of%20less%20than%2018%20per%20cent.%20Except%20for%20a%20decent%20performance%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20party%20flopped%20in%20other%20states.%20His%20strategy%20of%20targeting%20big%20business%20failed%20to%20resonate%20with%20voters%2C%20even%20when%20national%20sentiment%20had%20turned%20against%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lesson%20here%20for%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20VP%20Singh%20playbook%20of%20taking%20sides%20in%20corporate%20rivalries.%20While%20it%20may%20align%20you%20with%20one%20group%20over%20others%2C%20anti-business%20sentiment%20doesn't%20find%20many%20supporters%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimitations%20Of%20Mandal%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20VP%20Singh%20wore%20the%20badge%20of%20Mr.%20Clean.%20As%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20be%20a%20social%20justice%20messiah%20by%20implementing%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20reserving%2027%20per%20cent%20government%20jobs%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMandal%20politics%26quot%3B%20had%20a%20lasting%20impact%20on%20India's%20political%20dynamics.%20The%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20its%20various%20state-specific%20factions%20did%20win%20elections%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20Karnataka.%20However%2C%20these%20parties%20struggled%20with%20a%20significant%20electoral%20handicap%20-%20they%20never%20managed%20to%20secure%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20the%20total%20votes%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20led%20by%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20exponents%20of%20Mandal%20politics%2C%20couldn't%20overcome%20this%20limitation.%20The%20RJD's%20best-ever%20Lok%20Sabha%20performance%20was%20in%202004%20when%20it%20won%2022%20seats%20with%20a%20vote%20share%20of%20nearly%2031%20per%20cent.%20In%20assembly%20polls%2C%20its%20best%20performance%20was%20in%202000%2C%20with%20just%20over%2028%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20another%20advocate%20of%20Mandal%20politics%2C%20faced%20similar%20challenges.%20Its%20highest%20vote%20share%20was%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls%2C%20when%20it%20secured%20just%20over%2032%20percent%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EState-specific%20iterations%20of%20Mandal%20politics%2C%20such%20as%20the%20RJD%20and%20the%20SP%2C%20failed%20to%20garner%20support%20from%20all%20OBC%20groups.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20significant%20section%20of%20less%20dominant%20and%20more%20deprived%20OBCs%20grew%20dissatisfied%20with%20this%20brand%20of%20politics.%20This%20disenchanted%20group%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20BJP's%20resounding%20victories%20in%20the%202014%20and%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Data%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20(CSDS)%20shows%20that%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20numerically%20significant%20non-dominant%20OBCs%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20another%20point%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20must%20be%20wise%20to.%20The%20yet-to-be-published%202011%20caste%20census%20reportedly%20revealed%20approximately%2046%20lakh%20caste%20categories%2C%20as%20reported%20in%20leading%20newspapers%20at%20the%20time.%20Assuming%20that%20roughly%20half%20of%20these%20categories%20belong%20to%20the%20OBCs%2C%20in%20proportion%20to%20their%20population%20share%2C%20it%20means%20that%20when%20we%20refer%20to%20OBCs%2C%20we%20are%20essentially%20talking%20about%20a%20diverse%20group%20of%2015-20%20lakh%20social%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEach%20group%20has%20distinct%20challenges%20and%20aspirations.%20Their%20political%20allegiances%20depend%20on%20what%20is%20on%20offer.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20is%20fierce%20competition%20among%20proximate%20castes%20or%20groups%20closer%20to%20each%20other%20in%20the%20traditional%20hierarchy.%20Attempting%20to%20unify%20them%20under%20one%20banner%20and%20expecting%20them%20to%20vote%20together%20may%20be%20unrealistic.%20That%20is%20why%20Mandal%20parties%20had%20limited%20appeal%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20that%20is%20unlikely%20to%20change%20anytime%20soon.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20bear%20this%20in%20mind%20when%20applying%20the%20VP%20Singh%20playbook%20from%20the%20late%201980s%20and%20early%201990s%20in%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20a%20disclaimer%20and%20a%20related%20observation%20that%20made%20me%20rethink%20the%20electoral%20appeal%20of%20Mandal%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20have%20seen%20the%20Mandal%20phenomenon%20altering%20the%20basic%20grammar%20of%20India's%20politics%20in%20ways%20not%20much%20else%20could.%20That%20is%20the%20reason%20I%20anticipated%20a%20significant%20buzz%20the%20day%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20data%20was%20released.%20One%20way%20to%20gauge%20this%20was%20by%20examining%20Google%20Trend%20data%20on%20that%20day.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20among%20the%20top%20searches%20in%20India%20that%20day%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20ranked%20a%20low%2013.%20Even%20a%20nondescript%20cricket%20match%20and%20the%20wedding%20of%20Pakistani%20actress%20Mahira%20Khan%20caught%20more%20attention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Mayank%20Mishra%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%2C%20NDTV.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698235740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fnc7s9fh_rahul-gandhi-_625x300_09_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhi-needs-to-know-mandal-2-has-limited-appeal-4511843%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20have%20seen%20the%20Mandal%20phenomenon%20altering%20the%20basic%20grammar%20of%20India's%20politics%20in%20ways%20not%20much%20else%20could.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22h