ey%20next%20face%20South%20Africa%20on%20Friday%20and%20they%20must%20win%20that%20match%20to%20keep%20their%20semi-final%20hopes.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpoints-table%5C%22%3EWorld%20Cup%202023%20points%20table%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20such%20a%20pressure%20situation%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20star%20player%20Mohammad%20Yousuf%20said%20that%20he%20heard%20Babar%20cried%20after%20the%20loss.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20the%20press%20conference%20and%20it%20seemed%20that%20Babar%20Azam%20is%20under%20pressure.%20I%20heard%20Babar%20Azam%20cried%20too.%20We%20are%20with%20Babar%20Azam.%20We%20don't%20lose%20due%20to%20one%20individual%2C%20it's%20a%20team%20game.%20If%20we%20would%20have%20been%20in%20the%20team%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20our%20responsibility%20too.%20Win%20and%20loss%20is%20part%20of%20the%20game%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Ypusuf%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFi7KfDOXuuk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamaa%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20sad%20looking%20at%20Babar%2C%20He%20should%20not%20take%20too%20much%20stress.%20They%20should%20focus%20on%20next%20four%20matches.%20The%20entire%20nation%20is%20with%20him.%20But%20we%20need%20to%20analyse%20some%20things%20honestly.%20We%20were%2050-60%20runs%20short%20against%20Afghanistan%20on%20a%20good%20pitch.%20It%20seemed%20like%20Pakistan%20were%20facing%20Muralitharan.%20These%20are%20normal%20bowlers.%20Our%20fielding%20and%20bowling%20was%20also%20not%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan%20captain%20Babar%20Azam%20admitted%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20hurt%26quot%3B%20after%20his%20team%20was%20stunned%20in%20an%20eight-wicket%20defeat%20by%20Afghanistan%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%20on%20Monday%20which%20put%20their%20semi-finals%20hopes%20in%20peril.%20Afghanistan%20achieved%20their%20first-ever%20one-day%20victory%20over%20Pakistan%20in%20eight%20attempts%20as%20they%20chased%20down%20a%20283-run%20target%20with%20an%20over%20to%20spare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20hurt%20as%20a%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Azam%20whose%20side%20now%20have%20three%20defeats%20and%20two%20wins%20in%20five%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20face%20a%20formidable%20South%20Africa%20at%20the%20same%20Chennai%20venue%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20feel%20the%20disappointment%20and%20my%20message%20to%20my%20team%20for%20the%20remaining%20matches%20will%20be%20to%20learn%20from%20this%20defeat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Azam%2C%20whose%2074%20off%2095%20balls%20aided%20by%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abdullah%20Shafique%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113281-abdullah-shafique-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbdullah%20Shafique%3C%2Fa%3E's%2058%20guided%20Pakistan%20to%20282-7%20after%20they%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20batted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20achieved%20what%20we%20set%20out%20to%20do%20when%20we%20batted%20but%20we%20were%20not%20up%20to%20the%20mark%20in%20bowling%20and%20fielding%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Azam%20whose%20bowlers%20conceded%2017%20boundaries%20in%20the%20first%2016%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20failed%20to%20put%20them%20under%20pressure%20but%20I%20congratulate%20Afghanistan%20for%20this%20victory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20AFP%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698234900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fvu0bbh4o_babar-azam_625x300_23_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fheard-babar-azam-cried-pakistan-greats-sensational-claim-on-under-fire-captain-after-afghanistan-loss-4512717%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20things%20don't%20go%20their%20way%20in%20the%20remaining%20matches%20of%20the%20league%20stage%2C%20the%20Babar%20Azam-led%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%