e%20aspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20federal%20lawsuit%20accuses%20Meta%20of%20%26quot%3Bexploiting%26quot%3B%20young%20users%20by%20creating%20a%20business%20model%20designed%20to%20maximise%20the%20time%20they%20spend%20on%20the%20platform%20despite%20harm%20to%20their%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResearch%20has%20shown%20that%20young%20people's%20use%20of%20Meta's%20social%20media%20platforms%20is%20associated%20with%20depression%2C%20anxiety%2C%20insomnia%2C%20interference%20with%20education%20and%20daily%20life%2C%20and%20many%20other%20negative%20outcomes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20has%20given%20a%20free%20ride%20to%20these%20platforms.%20The%20US%20in%20particular%2C%20and%20it%20is%20time%20to%20take%20a%20re-look%20at%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlatforms%20must%20be%20much%20more%20accountable.%20Who%20is%20allowed%20to%20host%20content.%20I%20think%20days%20of%20this%20free%20pass%20and%20immunity%20are%20over.%20This%20is%20our%20government's%20intention%20as%20well...%C2%A0%20We%20must%20wake%20up%20to%20reality%20that%20there%20is%20harm%20and%20criminality%20lurking%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20the%20Indian%20government%20will%20ensure%20protection%20for%20its%20citizens%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20all%20platforms%20to%20follow%20rules.%20They%20are%20sent%20notices%20under%20IT%20rules.%20If%20they%20don't%20respond%2C%20consequences%20under%20law%20will%20follow.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%20came%20under%20the%20lens%20of%20US%20investigators%20after%20a%20Facebook%20whistleblower%2C%20Frances%20Haugen%2C%20leaked%20internal%20documents%20that%20sparked%20criticism%20that%20the%20social%20media%20giant%20had%20put%20profit%20before%20the%20security%20of%20its%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFacebook%2C%20she%20alleged%2C%20has%20failed%20to%20curtail%20toxic%20content%20and%20cannot%20be%20trusted%20to%20change%20its%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20that%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20keeping%20teens%20safe%20online%20and%20has%20introduced%20more%20than%2030%20tools%20to%20support%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20suit%20and%20that%20the%20states%20were%20not%20working%20with%20social%20media%20companies%20to%20create%20age-appropriate%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698233520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F434jgflo_rajeev-chandrasekhar-ndtv-650-_650x400_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdays-of-free-pass-immunity-over-it-minister-on-meta-being-sued-in-us-4512306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20today%20that%20the%20days%20of%20%26quot%3Bfree%20pass%26quot%3B%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%20are%20over%20and%20strict%20accountability%20will%20be%20enforced%20here%20on%20across%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdays-of-free-pass-immunity-over-it-minister-on-meta-being-sued-in-us-4512306%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdays-of-free-pass-immunity-over-it-minister-on-meta-being-sued-in-us-4512306%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdays-of-free-pass-immunity-over-it-minister-on-meta-being-sued-in-us-4512306%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raj%20Kundra%20opens%20up%20about%20dark%20times%20in%20prison%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698233307000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104699554%2Cimgsize-35366.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fraj-kundra-opens-up-about-dark-times-in-prison-reveals-shilpa-shettys-suggestion-to-move-abroad%2Farticleshow%2F104698550.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104698550.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERaj%20Kundra%2C%20who%20recently%20served%20a%20two-month%20prison%20sentence%20for%20a%20pornography%20case%2C%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20dark%20times%20in%20prison.%20He%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20considered%20ending%20his%20life%20during%20that%20challenging%20period.%20His%20wife%2C%20Shilpa%20Shetty%2C%20had%20suggested%20moving%20abroad%20to%20escape%20the%20turmoil%2C%20but%20Kundra%20decided%20to%20stay%20in%20India.%20He%20also%20shared%20the%20emotional%20distress%20he%20endured%20and%20the%20impact%20it%20had%20on%20his%20family.%20Despite%20his%20difficult%20experiences%2C%20Kundra%20is%20now%20set%20to%20make%20his%20acting%20debut%20in%20a%20satirical%20film%20inspired%20by%20his%20time%20in%20prison.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fraj-kundra-opens-up-about-dark-times-in-prison-reveals-shilpa-shettys-suggestion-to-move-abroad%2Farticleshow%2F104698550.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Hospital%20Rejects%20Report%20On%20HIV%20Infections%20In%20Thalassemia%20Child%20Patients%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20political%20storm%20has%20erupted%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20over%20a%20news%20report%20that%20said%2014%20children%20suffering%20from%20Thalassemia%20had%20tested%20positive%20for%20serious%20infections%20during%20screening%20at%20a%20Kanpur%20hospital.%20The%20hospital's%20top%20authority%20has%20trashed%20the%20report%2C%20saying%20a%20probe%20has%20been%20ordered%20against%20a%20doctor%20for%20allegedly%20spreading%20rumours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Hindustan%20Times%20report%20had%20said%2014%20children%20suffering%20from%20Thalassemia%20had%20tested%20positive%20for%20infections%20such%20as%20Hepatitis%20B%2C%20Hepatitis%20C%20and%20HIV%20during%20a%20screening%20at%20Kanpur's%20Lala%20Lajpat%20Rai%20Hospital.%20The%20report%20quoted%20Dr%20Arun%20Kumar%20Arya%2C%20head%20of%20the%20paediatrics%20department%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20concern%20and%20that%20the%20HIV%20infections%20were%20particularly%20worrying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20prompted%20a%20sharp%20attack%20by%20Opposition%20leaders%20on%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bdouble-engine%26quot%3B%20government%20has%20made%20health%20infrastructure%20%26quot%3Bdoubly%20sick%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BDouble%20engine%26quot%3B%20government%20is%20a%20term%20frequently%20used%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20their%20poll%20campaigns%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20twin%20advantage%20of%20having%20a%20BJP%20government%20at%20both%20the%20state%20and%20the%20centre%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20chief%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20this%20gross%20negligence%20is%20%26quot%3Bshameful%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BInnocent%20children%20are%20facing%20punishment%20for%20this%20unforgivable%20crime%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20main%20Opposition%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20said%20no%20one%20is%20watching%20the%20health%20services%20in%20the%20state.%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20the%20matter%20should%20be%20immediately%20probed%20and%20those%20responsible%20should%20be%20punished.%20The%20party's%20official%20handle%20blamed%20the%20state%20health%20department%20and%20minister%20Brijesh%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThalassemia%20is%20an%20inherited%20blood%20disorder%20due%20to%20which%20the%20body%20doesn't%20make%20enough%20haemoglobin.%20Patients%20suffering%20from%20this%20condition%20need%20frequent%20blood%20transfusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Mr%20Arya%20clarified%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20that%20the%20infections%20took%20place%20over%20a%20period%20of%20at%20least%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChildren%20suffering%20from%20Thalassemia%20need%20blood%20transfusions%20every%20three-four%20weeks.%20Blood%20transfusions%20come%20with%20risks%20of%20HIV%2C%20malaria%2C%20Hepatitis%20B%2C%20Hepatitis%20C%20and%20malaria%20infections.%20We%20get%20a%20routine%20check-up%20of%20these%20children%20done%20every%20three-six%20months%20to%20detect%20any%20case%20of%20infection.%20This%20data%20covers%20a%20period%20of%2010%20years%2C%20it%20is%20not%20that%20these%20infections%20happened%20in%20six%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20doctor%20also%20said%20the%20hospital%20has%20a%20system%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20infections%20during%20blood%20transfusions.%20%26quot%3BThese%20children%20also%20get%20blood%20transfusions%20at%20other%20health%20facilities%20if%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20requirement.%20We%20cannot%20say%20when%20they%20were%20infected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20Ganesh%20Shankar%20Vidyarthi%20Memorial%20Medical%20College%2C%20under%20which%20the%20hospital%20operaties%2C%20has%20rejected%20the%20report.%20Principal%20Dr%20Sanjay%20Kala%20has%20said%20the%20hospital%20has%20not%20reported%20HIV%2C%20Hepatitis%20B%20or%20Hepatitis%20C%20infections%20in%20any%20Thalassemia%20patient%20after%202019.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20ordered%20an%20investigation%20against%20Dr%20Arun%20Kumar%20Arya%20for%20making%20incorrect%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698233280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fsm9ungho_hospital-generic_62