en%20facing%20a%20dilemma%3A%20should%20she%20apply%20for%20a%20Canadian%20study%20visa%20now%20or%20defer%20until%20the%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%20show%20signs%20of%20a%20recovery%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimran%E2%80%99s%20fears%20are%20not%20unfounded.%20Diplomatic%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20been%20in%20a%20downward%20spiral%20since%20mid-September%2C%20when%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20told%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20that%20Indian%20agents%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Canadian%20Sikh%20citizen%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Khalistan%20activist%20who%20was%20wanted%20in%20India%20for%20terrorism%20charges.%20India%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20and%20later%20shut%20down%20visa%20services%20to%20Canadian%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETensions%20escalated%20further%20on%20October%2019%2C%20after%20Canada%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-calls-canadas-consulate-move-unilateral-clarifies-parity-only-for-diplomats-in-capitals%5C%22%3Ecomplied%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20demand%20to%20withdraw%3C%2Fa%3E%2041%20diplomats%20posted%20in%20India%2C%20suspending%20consular%20services%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20cause%20delays%20in%20visa%20services%20and%20longer%20waits%20at%20the%20Canadian%20Embassy%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20in-person%20submissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimran%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20of%20now%2C%20my%20parents%20have%20asked%20me%20to%20first%20complete%20my%20IELTS%20coaching%20and%20get%20a%20good%20score.%20We%20will%20plan%20the%20study%20visa%20later.%20If%20the%20situation%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20does%20not%20improve%20by%20then%2C%20I%20will%20have%20to%20pursue%20graduation%20in%20Jalandhar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20IELTS%20test%20scores%20are%20valid%20for%20two%20years%2C%20Simran%20said%20many%20of%20her%20friends%20are%20also%20planni