97185.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Gets%20Postal%20Job%20After%2028-Year%20Wait%20Following%20Supreme%20Court%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwenty-eight%20years%20after%20a%20man%20applied%20for%20a%20job%20in%20the%20postal%20department%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ordered%20his%20appointment%20noting%20that%20there%20was%20an%20error%20in%20holding%20him%20ineligible%20for%20the%20post.%20Ankur%20Gupta%20had%20applied%20for%20the%20post%20of%20postal%20assistant%20in%201995.%20After%20being%20selected%20for%20pre-induction%20training%2C%20he%20was%20later%20excluded%20from%20the%20merit%20list%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20he%20completed%20intermediate%20education%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bvocational%20stream%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGupta%20along%20with%20other%20unsuccessful%20candidates%20moved%20the%20Central%20Administrative%20Tribunal%20which%20ruled%20in%20their%20favour%20in%201999.%20The%20postal%20department%20challenged%20the%20tribunal's%20order%20and%20approached%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%202000.%20The%20high%20court%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20in%202017%20and%20upheld%20the%20CAT's%20order.%20A%20review%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20high%20court%20which%20was%20also%20dismissed%20in%202021%2C%20following%20which%20the%20department%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20top%20court%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20justices%20Bela%20M%20Trivedi%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20said%20a%20candidate%20cannot%20claim%20a%20vested%20right%20to%20appointment%2C%20once%20he%20is%20included%20in%20the%20merit%20list%2C%20he%20has%20a%20limited%20right%20of%20being%20accorded%20a%20fair%20treatment.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20if%20the%20candidature%20is%20not%20rejected%20at%20the%20threshold%20and%20the%20candidate%20is%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20selection%20process%20and%20ultimately%20his%20name%20figures%20in%20the%20merit%20list%20though%20such%20candidate%20has%20no%20indefeasible%20right%20to%20claim%20appointment%2C%20he%20does%20have%20a%20limited%20right%20of%20being%20accorded%20fair%20and%20non-discriminatory%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20the%20employer%2C%20if%20it%20is%20a%20State%20within%20the%20meaning%20of%20Article%2012%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20would%20have%20no%20authority%20to%20act%20in%20an%20arbitrary%20manner%20and%20throw%20the%20candidate%20out%20without%20rhyme%20or%20reason.%20%26quot%3BThe%20employer-State%20being%20bound%20by%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20law%20places%20an%20obligation%2C%20nay%20duty%2C%20on%20such%20an%20employer%20to%20provide%20some%20justification%20by%20way%20of%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20The%20bench%20said%20if%20the%20department%20had%20declared%20Gupta%20as%20ineligible%20based%20on%20the%20appreciation%20of%20the%20educational%20qualification%20at%20the%20threshold%2C%20the%20situation%20would%20have%20entirely%20been%20different.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it%20was%20not%20at%20the%20threshold%20that%20the%20third%20respondent%20was%20considered%20ineligible.%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20factual%20narrative%20would%20reveal%2C%20the%20appellant%20had%20considered%20the%20third%20respondent%20eligible%2C%20allowed%20him%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20various%20tests%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20selection%20process%2C%20interviewed%20him%2C%20placed%20his%20name%20quite%20high%20in%20the%20merit%20list%2C%20and%20thereafter%20sent%20him%20for%2015%20days'%20pre-induction%20training%20starting%20from%2015th%20March%2C%201996%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInvoking%20its%20extraordinary%20jurisdiction%20under%20Article%20142%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20top%20court%20directed%20that%20Gupta%20be%20offered%20appointment%2C%20initially%20on%20probation%2C%20on%20a%20post%20of%20Postal%20Assistant%20(for%20which%20he%20was%20selected)%20within%20a%20month%20and%20if%20no%20post%20is%20vacant%2C%20a%20supernumerary%20post%20shall%20be%20created%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20Gupta%20has%20been%20discriminated%20against%20and%20arbitrarily%20deprived%20of%20fruit%20of%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubject%20to%20satisfactory%20completion%20of%20the%20period%20of%20probation%2C%20the%20third%20respondent%20shall%20be%20confirmed%20in%20service%3B%20Should%20service%20rendered%20during%20probation%20be%20considered%20not%20satisfactory%2C%20the%20appellant%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20proceed%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20not%20actually%20worked%2C%20the%20third%20respondent%20(Gupta)%20shall%20neither%20be%20entitled%20to%20arrears%20of%20salary%20nor%20shall%20he%20be%20entitled%20to%20claim%20seniority%20from%20the%20date%20of%20appointment%20of%20other%20candidates%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process%20of%201995%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698231960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-gets-postal-job-after-28-year-wait-following-supreme-court-order-4512566%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20postal%20department%20had%20held%20Ankur%20Gupta%20ineligible%20in%201995.%20He%20had%20challenged%20the%20decision%20in%20Central%20Administrative%20Tribunal%2C%20which%20rules%20in%20their%20favour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-gets-postal-job-after-28-year-wait-following-supreme-court-order-4512566%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-gets-postal-job-after-28-year-wait-following-supreme-court-order-4512566%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-gets-postal-job-after-28-year-wait-following-supreme-court-order-4512566%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Influencer%20Shares%20Her%20Body%20Started%20Eating%20Itself%20After%20Fat-Burning%20Shots%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBeatriz%20Amma%2C%20a%20fitness%20influencer's%20worst%20nightmare%20came%20true%20after%20she%20had%20a%20horrifying%20battle%20with%20a%20flesh-eating%20illness.%C2%A0At%20the%20age%20of%2023%2C%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20Ms%20Amma%20sought%20to%20achieve%20perfection%20at%20an%20upscale%20spa%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20where%20she%20spent%20%24800%20(approximately%20Rs%2066%2C000)%20on%20a%20treatment%20regimen%20involving%20a%20series%20of%20vitamin%20injections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20injections%2C%20which%20included%20a%20mixture%20of%20vitamins%20B1%20and%20C%2C%20combined%20with%20%26quot%3Bfast-dissolving%26quot%3B%20deoxycholic%20acid%2C%20were%20administered%2060%20times%20into%20her%20arms%2C%20back%2C%20and%20stomach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20treatment%2C%20Ms%20Amma's%20life%20took%20an%20unexpected%20turn.%20She%20shared%20with%20%3Cem%3EKennedy%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20developed%20welts%20on%20my%20skin%2C%20and%20they%20began%20appearing%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20injections%20had%20been%20administered...%20My%20entire%20body%20seemed%20to%20be%20self-destructing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20diagnosis%20was%20bleak-Mycobacterium%20abscessus%2C%20a%20well-known%20bacterial%20infection%20that%20leads%20to%20painful%20skin%20lesions.%20Medical%20professionals%20attributed%20it%20to%20the%20improper%20injection%20of%20deoxycholic%20acid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Amma%2C%20a%20former%20swimsuit%20model%2C%20her%20aspirations%20of%20becoming%20a%20fitness%20influencer%20and%20enjoying%20a%20life%20filled%20with%20travel%20crumbled.%20She%20has%20undergone%20multiple%20surgeries%20to%20excise%20infected%20tissue%20and%20now%2C%20three%20years%20later%2C%20must%20endure%20six%20hours%20of%20daily%20intravenous%20antibiotic%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20to%20the%20chilling%20nature%20of%20this%20narrative%20is%20that%20everything%20appeared%20entirely%20legitimate.%20The%20Los%20Angeles%20spa%20where%20Amma%20received%20these%20injections%20exuded%20an%20aura%20of%20cleanliness%2C%20professionalism%2C%20and%20safety.%20%26quot%3BAn%20employee%20assured%20me%20it%20was%20produced%20by%20a%20highly%20reputable%20company%20and%20even%20displayed%20the%20vials%20to%20me.%20I%20was%20thrilled%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Amma%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrior%20research%20has%20demonstrated%20a%20troubling%20correlation%20between%20flawed%20injections%20and%20similar%20skin%20reactions%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20risks%20that%20individuals%20like%20Amma%20unwittingly%20assume%20in%20their%20pursuit%20of%20aesthetic%20enhancements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ensuing%20ordeal%20became%20a%20life-and-death%20struggle%2C%20with%20Amma%20bedridden%2C%20her%20own%20body%20seemingly%20turning%20against%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20even%20dress%20myself.%20I%20required%20assistance%20to%20use%20the%20restroom%2C%20shower%2C%20and%20change.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20deteriorating%20in%20bed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20recounted%2C%20describing%20how%20her%20body%20was%20ravaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Amma%20vividly%20recollects%20the%20moment%20when%20she%20feared%20she%20might%20succumb%20to%20the%20flesh-eating%20disease.%20%26quot%3BI%20prayed%20to%20God%20and%20said%2C%20'If%20this%20is%20my%20time%2C%20take%20me.'%20My%20body%20had%20reached%20its%20limit.%20I%20distinctly%20remember%20being%20in%20such%20excruciating%20pain%20that%20I%20believed%20I%20might%20not%20survive%20that%20night.%20I%20couldn't%20fight%20any%20longer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20time%20I%20gaze%20into%20the%20mirror%2C%20I'm%20reminded%20of%20how%20much%20of%20my%20life%20has%20been%20lost%20to%20this%20ordeal.%20My%20dream%20was%20to%20become%20a%20fitness%20influencer%2C%20and%20I%20cherished%20travelling%20and%20wearing%20bikinis.%20I%20had%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20attain%20the%20body%20I%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20lamented.%20Her%20doctors%20have%20informed%20her%2C%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20have%20this%20condition%20indefinitely%3B%20relinquish%20your%20aspirations%20of%20being%20an%20influencer%2C%20and%20your%20skin%20will%20constantly%20alarm%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Amma%20refuses%20to%20allow%20this%20traumatic%20experience%20to%20shape%20her%20identity.%20Instead%2C%20she%20directs%20her%20efforts%20toward%20promoting%20body%20positivity%20and%20increasing%20awareness%20of%20this%20disfiguring%20ailment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20her%20ongoing%20struggle%20with%20the%20repercussions%20of%20that%20ill-fated%20spa%20visit%20persists.%20She%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20now%20in%20the%20third%20year%20of%20this%20journey%2C%20and%20it's%20far%20from%20concluded.%20I%20never%20would%20have%20imagined%20that%20something%20as%20seemingly%20straightforward%20could%20nearly%20claim%20my%20life%20and%20leave%20me%20still%20grappling%20for%20survival.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698231840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fhsc5r518_beatriz-amma_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffitness-influencer-shares-her-body-started-eating-itself-after-fat-dissolving-injections-4512544%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20injections%20included%20a%20mixture%20of%20vitamins%20B1%20and%20C%20and%20%26quot%3Bfast-dissolving%26quot%3B%20deoxycholic%20acid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffitness-influencer