3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-restaurant-charging-diners-for-misbehaving-kids-slammed-online-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698231435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538ec540487ff031cad9fc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-restaurant-charging-diners-for-misbehaving-kids-slammed-online-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20restaurant%20near%20Blue%20Ridge%2C%20Georgia%20has%20been%20criticized%20on%20Reddit%20for%20adding%20an%20%26quot%3Badult%20surcharge%26quot%3B%20for%20parents%20whose%20kids%20don't%20behave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-restaurant-charging-diners-for-misbehaving-kids-slammed-online-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22School%20Textbooks%20To%20Have%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20Instead%20Of%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%3F%20What%20NCERT%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20replaced%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20school%20textbooks%20for%20all%20classes%2C%20a%20high-level%20committee%20for%20social%20sciences%2C%20constituted%20by%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%20to%20revise%20the%20school%20curriculum%2C%20has%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20committee%20chairperson%20C%20I%20Isaac%2C%20the%20panel%20has%20suggested%20replacing%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20textbooks%2C%20introducing%20%26quot%3Bclassical%20history%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3Bancient%20history%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20the%20curriculum%20and%20including%20the%20Indian%20Knowledge%20System%20(IKS)%20in%20the%20syllabus%20for%20all%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENCERT%20Chairman%20Dinesh%20Saklani%2C%20however%2C%20said%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20yet%20on%20the%20panel's%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20has%20unanimously%20recommended%20that%20the%20name%20'Bharat'%20should%20be%20used%20in%20the%20textbooks%20for%20students%20across%20classes.%20We%20have%20also%20recommended%20introducing%20classical%20history%20instead%20of%20ancient%20history%20in%20the%20textbooks%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaac%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBharat%20is%20an%20age-old%20name.%20The%20name%20Bharat%20has%20been%20used%20in%20ancient%20texts%2C%20such%20as%20Vishnu%20Purana%2C%20which%20is%207%2C000%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaac%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20Bharat%20first%20appeared%20officially%20when%20the%20government%20sent%20out%20G20%20invites%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20Bharat%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Later%2C%20the%20nameplate%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20also%20read%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsaac%20said%20the%20committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20highlighting%20%26quot%3BHindu%20victories%26quot%3B%20in%20various%20battles%20in%20the%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20failures%20are%20presently%20mentioned%20in%20the%20textbooks.%20But%20our%20victories%20over%20the%20Mughals%20and%20sultans%20are%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Isaac%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Historical%20Research%20(ICHR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20British%20had%20divided%20Indian%20history%20into%20three%20phases%20--%20ancient%2C%20medieval%20and%20modern%20--%20showing%20India%20in%20darkness%2C%20unaware%20of%20scientific%20knowledge%20and%20progress.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20classical%20period%20of%20Indian%20history%20be%20taught%20in%20schools%2C%20along%20with%20medieval%20and%20modern%20periods%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NCERT%20is%20revising%20the%20curriculum%20of%20the%20school%20textbooks%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%20The%20council%20recently%20constituted%20a%2019-member%20National%20Syllabus%20and%20Teaching%20Learning%20Material%20Committee%20(NSTC)%20to%20finalise%20the%20curriculum%2C%20textbooks%20and%20learning%20material%20for%20these%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Indian%20Knowledge%20System%20(IKS)%20in%20the%20curriculum%20of%20all%20subjects%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaac%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20include%20ICHR%20Chairperson%20Raghuvendra%20Tanwar%2C%20Vandana%20Mishra%2C%20Professor%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%2C%20Vasant%20Shinde%2C%20former%20vice-chancellor%20of%20the%20Deccan%20College%20Deemed%20University%2C%20and%20Mamta%20Yadav%2C%20who%20teaches%20sociology%20in%20a%20Haryana%20government%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698231300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F5jmh35jk_ncert-650_625x300_18_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fschool-textbooks-to-have-bharat-instead-of-india-what-ncert-said-4512288%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NCERT%20is%20revising%20the%20curriculum%20of%20the%20school%20textbooks%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fschool-textbooks-to-ha