cted%20a%20collision%2C%20attempted%20to%20pull%20over%2C%20traveling%2020%20feet%20at%20a%20speed%20of%207%20mph%20while%20the%20pedestrian%20was%20still%20underneath%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DMV%20said%20that%20its%20representatives%20met%20with%20Cruise%20the%20following%20day%20and%20were%20shown%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20accident%20captured%20by%20the%20robotaxi's%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20said%20that%20the%20self-driving%20company%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20footage%20of%20the%20car%20attempting%20to%20pull%20over%20immediately%20after%20the%20crash%2C%20and%20only%20provided%20it%20several%20days%20later%20at%20the%20DMV's%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20subsequent%20maneuvering%20of%20the%20vehicle%20indicates%20that%20Cruise's%20vehicles%20may%20lack%20the%20ability%20to%20respond%20in%20a%20safe%20and%20appropriate%20manner%20during%20incidents%20involving%20a%20pedestrian%20so%20as%20not%20to%20unnecessarily%20put%20the%20pedestrian%20or%20others%20at%20risk%20of%20further%20injury%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DMV%20wrote%2C%20per%20Vice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Vice%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Cruise%20disputed%20the%20DMV's%20report.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20confirm%20that%20Cruise%20showed%20the%20full%20video%20to%20the%20DMV%20on%20October%203rd%2C%20and%20played%20it%20multiple%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20reached%20out%20to%20Cruise%20for%20further%20comment%20but%20didn't%20immediately%20hear%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruise%20has%20been%20a%20controversial%20presence%20in%20San%20Francisco%20ever%20since%20it%20received%20approval%20to%20run%20its%20robotaxi%20service%2024%2F7%20in%20the%20city%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20cars%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20several%20accidents%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2023%2F8%2F18%2F23837217%2Fcruise-robotaxi-driverless-crash-fire-truck-san-francisco%5C%22%2