20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20you%20do%20not%20need%20to%20scratch%20deep%20to%20reveal%20it's%20myth%2C%20USTs%20appeal%20still%20looks%20enduring%2C%26quot%3B%20they%C2%A0%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slide%20in%20China's%20Treasury%20holdings%20attracted%20much%20attention%20particularly%20as%20the%20declines%20accelerated%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20a%20time%20when%20US%20bonds%20have%20been%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20historic%20rout.%20The%20selloff%20saw%20benchmark%2010-year%20yields%20more%20than%20triple%20since%20the%20end-2021%20to%20breach%20the%20psychologically%20important%205%25%20mark%20this%20week%2C%20fueled%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20aggressive%20interest-rate%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20longer%20term%2C%20any%20deterioration%20in%20relations%20between%20the%20West%20and%20rival%20countries%20such%20as%20China%20could%20actually%20boost%20demand%20for%20the%20safe-haven%20appeal%20of%20Treasuries%2C%20according%20to%20the%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20value%20on%20being%20able%20to%20hold%20assets%20(directly%20or%20indirectly)%20in%20democracies%20bound%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20The%20more%20autocratic%20non-democratic%20regimes%20become%2C%20the%20more%20appealing%20assets%20in%20safe%20havens%20will%20be.%20That%20is%20clearly%20visible%20in%20the%20constant%20march%20of%20private%20sector%20cash%20into%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20and%20team%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-china-plot-against-usd-bonds-treasurys-is-a-myth-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698228367000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6536be7796908fd7cdb563ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fdedollarization-china-plot-against-usd-bonds-treasurys-is-a-my