cting%20cells%2C%20giving%20them%20the%20ability%20to%20combat%20cancer%20cells.%20%26quot%3BTo%20see%20that%20all%20of%20the%20hard%20work%20paid%20off%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20was%20really%20a%20surreal%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Heman%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20idea%20came%20when%20he%20was%20living%20in%20Ethiopia%20where%20he%20saw%20people%20constantly%20working%20and%20exposed%20to%20the%20sun.%20Although%20he%20didn't%20pay%20attention%20to%20it%2C%20when%20the%20competition%20dates%20neared%2C%20he%20recalled%20his%20time%20there%20and%20decided%20to%20focus%20his%20research%20on%20skin%20cancer.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20make%20my%20idea%20something%20that%20not%20only%20was%20great%20in%20terms%20of%20science%20but%20also%20could%20be%20accessible%20to%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%20Heman%20added%20that%20he%20wanted%20his%20product%20to%20be%20as%20much%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bconstant%26quot%3B%20in%20people's%20lives%20as%20possible%20and%20therefore%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bmost%20convenient%20and%20most%20trustworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%2C%20after%20being%20selected%20in%20the%20top%2010%20category%2C%20was%20paired%20with%20a%20mentor%20Deborah%20Isabelle%2C%20who%20is%20a%203M%20product%20engineering%20specialist.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20teenager%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20on%20making%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place%20for%20people%20he%20hasn't%20necessarily%20even%20met%20yet%26quot%3B%20and%20could%20see%20his%20passion%20in%20their%20first%20meeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20months%20of%20experimentation%20were%20required%20to%20develop%20a%20prototype%20that%20had%20a%20blend%20of%20compounds%20that%20would%20be%20functional.%20Heman%20worked%20out%20the%20formula%20for%20the%20soap%20prototype%20he%20was%20going%20to%20present%20at%20the%20championship%20using%20computer%20modelling.%20The%20soap%2C%20which%20is%20named%20Skin%20Cancer%20Treating%20Soap%2C%20works%20by%20%26quot%3Busing%20a%20compound%20that%20helps%20revive%20dendritic%20cells%2C%20which%20are%20killed%20by%20cancer%20cells.%20Once%20the%20dendritic%20cells%20are%20revived%2C%20they%20are%20able%20to%20then%20fight%20against%20the%20cancer%20cells%26quot%3B.%20As%20per%20Isabelle%2C%20this%20%26quot%3Breactivates%20the%20body's%20healing%20power%26quot%3B%20and%20reminds%20the%20body%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20defend%20itself%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHeman%20notes%20that%20although%20there%20are%20several%20creams%20in%20the%20market%2C%20a%20soap%20for%20treating%20cancer%20has%20never%20been%20used.%20He%20told%20the%20panel%20in%20the%20presentation%20that%20he%20told%20the%20panel%20he%20wishes%20to%20turn%20the%20soap%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbol%20of%20hope%2C%20accessibility%20and%20a%20world%20where%20skin%20cancer%20treatment%20is%20within%20reach%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698225720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fa05tekq8_heman-bekele_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-invents-soap-to-treat-skin-cancer-to-cost-less-than-10-4511922%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20told%20the%20panel%20in%20the%20presentation%20that%20he%20told%20the%20panel%20he%20wishes%20to%20turn%20the%20soap%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbol%20of%20hope%2C%20accessibility%20and%20a%20world%20where%20skin%20cancer%20treatment%20is%20within%20reach%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-invents-soap-to-treat-skin-cancer-to-cost-less-than-10-4511922%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-invents-soap-to-treat-skin-cancer-to-cost-less-than-10-4511922%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-invents-s