20dangerous%20step%20towards%20%5Bthe%5D%20politicisation%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20cross-section%20of%20veteran%20service%20officers%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20unashamedly%20exploiting%20the%20services%20for%20its%20political%20ends%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20and%20national%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20retired%20two-star%20IA%20officer%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20named%20as%20he%20feared%20repercussions%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20his%20continued%20pension%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20even%20more%20worrisome%20that%20such%20tactics%20are%20being%20effected%20with%20the%20concurrence%20of%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%20who%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20past%2C%20are%20anxious%20to%20please%20their%20political%20bosses%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWriting%20about%20one%20such%20initiative%20to%20blatantly%20promote%20government%20programmes%2C%20former%20Lieutenant%20General%20H.S.%20Panag%20declared%20that%20%E2%80%98deep%20selection%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98merit-driven%E2%80%99%20promotions%20in%20the%20services%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Farmy-cant-ask-soldiers-to-do-social-work-on-leave-its-beyond-the-call-of-duty%2F1750131%2F%5C%22%3Eweakened%20the%20will%20of%20the%20top%20brass%20to%20deter%20political%20and%20non-constitutional%20designs%20of%20the%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20tongue-in-cheek%20reference%20to%20promotions%20was%2C%20obviously%2C%20to%20higher%20rank%20elevation%20via%20political%20patronage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi%20Government%20Move%20to%20Turn%20Government%20Officers%20into%20%E2%80%98Rath%20Prabharis%E2%80%99%20Stirs%20Storm%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3EModi%20Government%20Move%20to%20Turn%20Gover