Screenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM-1024x642.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20selfie%20point%20at%20Rajghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20IA%20and%20the%20United%20Services%20Institution%20(USI)%20think%20tank%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Udbhav%20aims%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetailm.aspx%3FPRID%3D1969684%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20(PIB)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20exploit%20India%E2%80%99s%205%2C000-year%20old%20civilisational%20legacy%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehend%20its%20enduring%20connect%2C%20relevance%20and%20applicability%20in%20the%20modern%20day%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20bequest%20includes%20studying%2C%20examining%20and%20analysing%20the%20writings%20of%20Chanakya%20(%3Cem%3EArthashastra%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20post-Mauryan%20Kamandaka%20(%3Cem%3ENitisara%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20those%20of%20the%20Tamil%20saint-poet%20Thiruvalluvar%20(%3Cem%3ETirukkural%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20all%20of%20which%20the%20PIB%20incredulously%20declared%20%E2%80%9C%5Balign%5D%20with%20modern%20military%20codes%20of%20ethics%20or%20just%20war%20and%20principles%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Convention%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20goes%20on%20to%20state%20that%20Udbhav%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvisionary%20initiative%20by%20the%20%5BIA%5D%E2%80%9D%20seeking%20to%20%E2%80%9Cintegrate%20age-old%20wisdom%20with%20contemporary%20military%20pedagogy%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20enhancing%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%20thinking%2C%20statecraft%20and%20warfare%E2%80%9D.%20In%20short%2C%20Udbhav%2C%20according%20to%20the%20MoD%20and%20the%20government%2C%20is%20poised%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfoster%20deeper%20understanding%E2%80%9D%20of%20military%20matters%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccontribu