0executing%20Indian%20military%20strategy%20was%20%E2%80%9Csub-par%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cirrelevant%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Crelegated%20to%20a%20distant%20memory%20with%20rediscovered%20ancient%20wisdom%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNothing%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20General%20Dhanoa%2C%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth%20in%20the%20framing%20of%20modern-day%20military%20strategy%20and%20the%20need%20to%20have%20a%20common%20doctrinal%20thread%20that%20binds%20the%20tactical%20to%20the%20strategic%20in%20our%20expected%20joint%20theatre%20commands%20of%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%20Besides%2C%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20remain%20alive%20to%20the%20doctrinal%20precepts%20of%20modern-day%20conflict%20that%20required%20%E2%80%9Ckeen%20study%20of%20current%20military%20thought%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20categorically%20advised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20earlier%2C%20the%20MoD%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefence-ministry-selfie-points-narendra-modi%5C%22%3Edirected%20the%20establishment%20of%20geo-tagged%20selfie%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20all%20its%20various%20departments%20and%20related%20organisations%20to%20%E2%80%98showcase%E2%80%99%20the%20achievements%20or%20good%20works%20executed%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20military%20realm%20over%20the%20past%20nine%20years%20it%20had%20been%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20822%20such%20selfie%20points%2C%20that%20were%20likely%20to%20carry%20a%20photograph%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20much%20like%20the%20former%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20certificates%20and%20more%20recently%20like%20the%20G20%20posters%2C%20which%20also%20sported%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20lotus%20logo%2C%20would%20be%20focused%20on%20Defence%20Public%20Sector%20Undertakings%2C%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%2C%20Sainik%20Schools%20and%20the%20National%20Cad