ll%20town%20and%20city%20neighbourhood%20communities%20by%20publicising%20the%20merits%20of%20assorted%20government%20welfare%20schemes%20like%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20and%20Sarva%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%20and%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20would%20be%20monitored%20by%20the%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20units%20through%20quarterly%20feedback%20supported%20by%20photographs%20and%20video%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20these%20%E2%80%98soldier%20ambassadors%E2%80%99%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20the%20IA%E2%80%99s%20Ceremonials%20and%20Welfare%20Directorate%20that%20functions%20under%20the%20adjutant%20general%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20forces%E2%80%99%20overall%20administration%2C%20to%20instruct%20their%20respective%20societies%20in%20patriotism%20and%20nationalism%2C%20hygiene%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20the%20perils%20of%20drug%20abuse%2C%20road%20safety%2C%20to%20motivate%20and%20mentor%20their%20youth%20and%20to%20organise%20sports%20events%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20military%20officials%20said%20that%20the%20Army%20Training%20Command%20in%20Shimla%20had%20issued%20formal%20guidelines%20for%20these%20soldiers%20to%20follow%20with%20regard%20to%20vindicating%20these%20%E2%80%98educative%E2%80%99%20tasks%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20%E2%80%98leveraging%E2%80%99%20their%20skills%20and%20innate%20discipline%20towards%20augmenting%20nation%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Panag%20estimates%20that%20at%20any%20given%20time%2C%20the%20armed%20forces%20will%20have%20some%20350%2C000%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20warriors%E2%80%9D%20engaged%20in%20various%20welfare%20activities%20at%20a%20time%2C%20in%20what%20he%20terms%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Farmy-cant-ask-soldiers-to-do-social-work-on-leave-its-beyond-the-call-of-duty%2F1750131%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20government-led%20social%20service%20drive%20ever%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20soldiers%20are%20entitled%20to%20two%20months%20leave%20annually%2C%20in%20addition%20to%2030%20days%20of%20casual%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpoliticising-the-armed-forces-has-consequences%5C%22%3EPoliticising%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Has%20Consequences%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20state%20that%20this%20scheme%20was%20being%20%E2%80%98forced%E2%80%99%20on%20soldiers%2C%20or%20an%20advisory%20would%20have%20sufficed%2C%20rather%20than%20structured%20directions%20to%20implement%20it.%20In%20military%20culture%2C%20the%20general%20says%2C%20recommendations%20of%20higher%20headquarters%20were%20tantamount%20to%20%E2%80%98orders%20to%20be%20obeyed%E2%80%99%20and%20argued%20that%20words%20had%20been%20cleverly%20juggled%20to%20make%20the%20scheme%20appear%20voluntary%20to%20ward%20off%20protests%20and%20court%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20adage%20that%20a%20soldier%20is%20never%20off%20duty%2C%20has%20been%20literally%20applied%E2%80%9D%2C%20General%20Panag%20said%20and%20dubbed%20the%20%E2%80%98social%20warrior%E2%80%99%20scheme%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversial%20both%20in%20concept%20and%20execution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20wider%20canvas%2C%20the%20Faustian%20bargain%20between%20the%20Indian%20soldier%20and%20politicians%20had%20intensified%20manifold%20in%20recent%20years.%20It%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20many%20senior%20service%20personnel%20are%20increasingly%20identifying%20themselves%20with%20the%20BJP-led%20administration%2C%20that%20in%20turn%20seeks%20to%20exploit%20military%20achievements%20for%20political%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20host%20of%20senior%20serving%20and%20retired%20military%20officers%20openly%20acknowledge%20that%20since%202014%2C%20%E2%80%98political%20expediency%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20factored%20into%20several%20of%20their%20tactical%20operational%20plans%20and%20wider%20strategic%20decisions.%20This%20symbiotic%