2%3A%22As%20Israel%20Kills%20Thousands%20of%20Civilians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Remember%20the%20'International%20Community'%20Helped%20It%20Do%20So%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17151101%2FF8PxlS-a4AAO8nS.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20unimpeded%20bloodbath%20continues%20apace.%20According%20to%20latest%20reports%20from%20several%20news%20agencies%2C%20more%20than%20700%20Gazan%20civilians%20were%20killed%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20October%2024%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%205500%20Gazan%20women%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-hamas-war-5000-killed-in-gaza-health-ministry-says%2Flive-67180974%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edue%20to%20deliver%20their%20babies%20this%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20are%20delivering%20on%20the%20streets%20as%20many%20hospitals%20are%20dysfunctional%20and%20most%20are%20hopelessly%20overcrowded.%20The%20siege%20imposed%20by%20Israel%20is%20denying%20water%2C%20food%2C%20medicine%20and%20fuel%20to%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDepriving%20a%20whole%20population%20of%20what%20is%20essential%20to%20survive%20is%20a%20crime%20against%20humanitay%20and%20demanding%20they%20evacuate%20their%20land%20constitutes%20ethnic%20cleansing%20%E2%80%93%20a%20war%20crime%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions%20and%20the%20Rome%20Statute%20of%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20jurisdiction%20over%20Palestinian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%2C%20Palestinians%20are%20unforgivably%20guilty%20of%20wanting%20to%20take%20back%20land%2C%20home%20and%20hearth%20stolen%20from%20them.%20Now%2C%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20heading%20an%20extreme%20right-wing%20government%20that%20includes%20fascists%20and%20religious%20zealots%2C%20minces%20no%20words%3A%20he%20seeks%20the%20eradication%20of%20Hamas%20which%20he%20characteriaes%20as%20a%20purely%20terrorist%20organization.%20But%20who%20is%20Hamas%3F%20Clearly%2C%20Israel%C2%A0%20does%20not%20plan%20on%20eradicating%20only%20militants%20and%20activists.%20No%20less%20an%20authority%20than%20the%20president%20of%20Israel%20had%20said%20there%20are%20no%20innocent%20people%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20bombing%20we%20are%20seeing%20is%20proof%20that%20this%20belief%20is%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20Israeli%20military%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAided%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community%E2%80%9D%20and%20other%20friendly%20states%20who%20also%20regard%20Hamas%20as%20nothing%20other%20than%20a%20terrorist%20organization%2C%20Gazans%20have%20been%20told%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%20they%20must%20leave%20the%20land%20so%20the%20Israeli%20war%20machine%20can%20go%20ahead%20and%20eliminate%20Hamas%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20problem%20is%20that%20Gaza%20is%20perhaps%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20densely%20populated%20strip%20of%20land%2C%20with%20all%20exits%20controlled%20by%20the%20Israelis%20%E2%80%93%20de%20jure%20or%20de%20facto%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Rafah%20crossing%20into%20Egypt%20is%20of%20course%20manned%20by%20Egypt%2C%20which%20questions%20with%20reason%20why%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community%E2%80%9D%20should%20expect%20Egypt%20to%20take%20in%20so%20many%20refugees%20when%20they%20themselves%20fight%20off%20little%20dribs%20and%20drabs%20of%20migrants%20and%20refugees%20from%20their%20borders%2C%20indifferent%20to%20the%20hundreds%20who%20end%20up%20drowning%20in%20the%20seas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20once%20taken%20in%2C%20who%20is%20to%20say%20that%20Israel%20will%20ever%20let%20them%20back%20in%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20day%2C%20they%20have%20not%20let%20in%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20who%20were%20ejected%20from%20Palestine%20after%20the%201948%20usurpation%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Nakba%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20active%20connivance%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20terrorism%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community%E2%80%9D%20should%20remember%20that%20the%20first%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D%20of%20modern%20history%20in%20West%20Asia%20were%20the%20Zionist%20Irgun%20gang%20who%20blew%20up%20the%20King%20David%20hotel%20in%20Jerusalem%20on%20July%2022%2C%201946%2C%20killing%2091%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20%E2%80%9Cact%20of%20insane%20terrorism%E2%80%9D%20(to%20use%20the%20words%20of%20Clement%20Atlee%2C%20British%20prime%20minister%20at%20the%20time)%20was%20preceded%20by%20several%20other%20acts%20of%20terrorism.%20The%20last%20chief%20of%20the%20Irgun%20gang%20was%20none%20other%20than%20Menachem%20Begin%2C%20later%20to%20become%20Israeli%20prime%20minister.%20You%20see%2C%20the%20ugly%20truth%20about%20terrorism%20is%20that%20terrorists%20who%20succeed%20in%20their%20projects%20can%20become%20prime%20ministers.%20Those%20who%20fail%20remain%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20Hindu%2C%20Prabhakaran%2C%20actively%20empathised%20with%20by%20many%20in%20India%20%2C%20succeeded%20in%20obtaining%20a%20%E2%80%9CTamil%20Elam%E2%80%9D%20he%20too%2C%20like%20Begin%2C%20could%20have%20become%20a%20prime%20minister%2C%20notwithstanding%20all%20the%20terrorist%20doings%20of%20the%20LTTE%2C%20including%20the%20assassination%20of%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20had%20Lenin%20or%20Castro%2C%20even%20Mandela%2C%20not%20succeeded%2C%20they%20would%20have%20remained%20reviled%20terrorists%2C%20no%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20a%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20a%20Chandrashekhar%20Azad%20and%20an%20Udham%20Singh%20would%20have%20if%20the%20British%20empire%20had%20not%20been%20defeated%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20anti-colonial%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20of%20course%2C%20those%20that%20support%20the%20Zionist%20warmongers%20find%20it%20convenient%20to%20date%20Palestinian%20history%20from%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20just%20as%20many%20in%20India%20nowadays%20count%20Indian%20independence%20from%202014.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20also%20recognize%20the%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20did%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20vacuum%2C%E2%80%9D%20UN%20secretary%20general%20Antonio%20Gutteres%20told%20the%20Security%20Council%20on%20October%2024.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%2056%20years%20of%20suffocating%20occupation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20who%20wish%20to%20live%20in%20what%20has%20been%20called%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20open-air%20prison%20have%20no%20safe%20place%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20to%20the%20two-state%20solution%20envisaged%20in%20the%20Balfour%20declaration%20of%201917%20which%20divided%20Palestine%2C%20and%20jointly%20reiterated%20in%20the%20Oslo%20accord%2C%20Jewish%20settlers%20are%20seeing%20to%20it%20in%20the%20Occupied%20West%20Bank%20that%20this%20will%20never%20come%20to%20pass%20with%20daily%20acts%20of%20violence%20including%20murder%2C%20vandalism%20and%20arson.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20nation%20state%20in%20modern%20history%20has%20defied%20as%20many%20resolutions%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%20as%20has%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98rules-based%20international%20order%E2%80%99%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community%E2%80%9D%20loves%20to%20talk%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20guilty%20party%20remain%20the%20Palestinians%20for%20their%20temerity%20and%20gumption%20to%20seek%20to%20reverse%20their%20dispossession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20the%20Ukrainians%2C%20for%20whom%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community%E2%80%9D%20has%20spared%20no%20money%20or%20materiel%20in%20their%20war%20to%20take%20back%20the%20eastern%20Donesk%20regions%20from%20occupation%20by%20the%20Russian%20Federation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20history%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community%E2%80%9D%20has%20taught%20us%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20this%3A%20sauce%20for%20the%20goose%20is%20never%2C%20or%20not%20necessarily%2C%20sauce%20for%20the%20gander.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESensible%20people%20accept%20what%20fate%20is%20delivered%20to%20them%20by%20God%E2%80%99s%20chosen%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20there%20exist%20thousands%20of%20non-Zionist%20Jews%20not%20just%20among%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20community%E2%80%9D%20but%20within%20Israel%20herself%20who%20have%20made%20bold%20to%20step%20out%20to%20denounce%20what%20they%20have%20called%20%E2%80%9CIsraeli%20apartheid.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20Holocaust%20survivors%20as%20well%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20demonstration%20in%20New%20York%20City%E2%80%99s%20Times%20Square%2C%20the%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20Organisation%20came%20out%20to%20say%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20in%20our%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%2C%20marching%20to%20the%20house%20of%20the%20Senate%20Majority%20leader%2C%20Chuck%20Schumer%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Fnyregion%2Fpalestine-protest-nyc-times-square.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemanded%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20better%20proof%20that%20Zionism%20as%20a%20political%20philosophy%20does%20not%20represent%20all%20Jewish%20people%2C%20just%20as%20Hamas%20does%20not%20represent%20all%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETailpiece%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%20despicable%20the%20assault%20of%20October%207%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israel%2C%20and%20however%20despicable%20the%20vengeance%20exacted%20by%20the%20Zionist%20war-machine%20on%20innocent%20Gazans%2C%20we%20need%20to%20remember%20the%20crude%20fact%20that%20both%20the%20extreme%20right-wingers%20in%20the%20current%20Israeli%20government%20and%20the%20Hamas%20were%20elected%20to%20their%20c