0colleges%20in%20India.%20Police%20officials%20of%20the%20city%20state%20that%20almost%2060%20percent%20students%20are%20from%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20being%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20parents%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20send%20their%20children%20here%2C%20which%20also%20lays%20heavily%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20these%2015-18-year-olds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20an%20agricultural%20background.%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20doctor%2C%20but%20seeing%20the%20other%20students%20here%2C%20who%20are%20equally%20good%2C%20many%20even%20better%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%E2%80%99ll%20even%20crack%20the%20exam.%20My%20parents%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20a%20paid%20seat.%20I%20might%20give%20the%20exam%20next%20year%20again%20if%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20clear%20it%20this%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoes%20he%20have%20any%20career%20plan%20if%20medicine%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20out%3F%20No%2C%20he%20emphasises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20only%20a%20few%20of%20the%20roughly%202%20lakh%20students%20who%20flock%20to%20Kota%20each%20year%20(figures%20as%20per%20Kota%20police%20officials)%2C%20would%20be%20able%20to%20get%20into%20these%20few%20top%20institutes.%20What%20happens%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20them%3F%20Do%20they%20have%20Plan%20Bs%3F%20Do%20our%20education%20systems%2C%20parents%2C%20teachers%20equip%20students%20to%20handle%20failure%20and%20teach%20them%20that%20there%20is%20a%20life%20beyond%20these%20courses%20and%20colleges.%20The%20answer%2C%20which%20today%E2%80%99s%20statistics%20show%2C%20is%20a%20big%20NO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKota%20has%20seen%20a%20rising%20number%20of%20suicides%20in%20this%20year%20alone%20with%20more%20than%2025%20students%20having%20taken%20their%20lives.%20Student%20suicides%20have%20increased%20across%20the%20country%20too.%20The%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20data%20states%20that%2013%2C089%20students%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%202021.%20This%20alarming%20increase%20in%20deaths%20by%20suicides%20has%20forced%20the%20administration%20in%20Kota%20and%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20to%20take%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20a%20few%20crusaders%20who%20are%20working%20towards%20identifying%20depression%20in%20students%20and%20telling%20them%20that%20life%20is%20much%20bigger%20than%20just%20one%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Have%20a%20Plan%20B%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ASP%20Chandrasheel%20Thakur%20speaking%20to%20students%20in%20Kota%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807-272x182.jpeg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332816%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EASP%20Chandrasheel%20Thakur%20speaking%20to%20students%20in%20Kota.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%2C%20a%20police%20team%20of%20the%20special%20student%20cell%20led%20by%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(ASP)%20Kota%2C%20Chandrasheel%20Thakur%2C%20who%20was%20specially%20called%20back%20to%20the%20city%20from%20Udaipur%20to%20handle%20this%20team%2C%20sets%20out%20to%20visit%20hostels%20and%20PG%20(paying%20guest)%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176333%2Fiit-alumnus-start-happiness-hostels-in-kota-to-prevent-suicides%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccommodations%20in%20Kota%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20plain%20clothes.%20Thakur%20was%20previously%20in%20Kota%20for%208%20years%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20on%20many%20youth%20outreach%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%2C%20and%20having%20kids%20of%20the%20same%20age%20or%20older%20at%20home%2C%20these%20male%20and%20female%20officers%20speak%20to%20students%20daily%20in%20an%20informal%20setting.%20They%20are%20part%20of%20the%20special%20student%20cell%20established%20in%20Kota%20on%2024%20June%202023%2C%20which%20has%20a%2024%C3%977%20helpline%20with%20three%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20questions%20like%20is%20anything%20bothering%20them%2C%20do%20they%20really%20want%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20or%20a%20doctor%20or%20if%20they%20able%20to%20understand%20what%20is%20being%20taught%20in%20class%20to%20other%20basic%20questions%20like%20do%20they%20like%20the%20food%20being%20served%20in%20the%20mess%2C%20these%20officers%20establish%20a%20rapport%20with%20the%20students%20to%20identify%20if%20they%20are%20at%20risk%20or%20if%20they%20are%20doing%20okay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20is%20working%20with%20students%2C%20identifying%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20and%20just%20offering%20a%20listening%20ear%20to%20them.%20We%20look%20for%20red%20flags%20or%20symptoms%20of%20depression%20when%20we%20interact%20with%20students.%20We%20speak%20to%20hostel%20wardens%2C%20mess%20staff%2C%20%3Cem%3Edabbawalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20understand%20which%20students%20are%20not%20eating%20properly%2C%20who%20is%20returning%20their%20tiffins%20without%20finishing.%20Food%20is%20a%20very%20important%20factor%20for%20these%20children.%20Once%20we%20identify%20these%20children%2C%20we%20speak%20one%20on%20one%20and%20guide%20them%20to%20counsellors%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cell%20also%20has%20a%20control%20room%20where%20police%20personnel%20are%20assigned%20to%20speak%20to%20callers.%20The%20ASP%20states%20that%20they%20receive%20almost%207%20calls%20everyday%20from%20students%20facing%20mental%20health%20issues.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20received%20over%20500%20serious%20calls%20in%20less%20than%20four%20months%2C%20highlighting%20how%20dire%20the%20situation%20is%20in%20Kota.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShashi%20Prakash%20Singh%2C%20a%20NEET%20coaching%20teacher%2C%20is%20on%20a%20sabbatical%20now%20to%20solely%20focus%20on%20counselling%20students.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20these%20suicides%20are%20an%20indicator%20of%20a%20larger%20mental%20health%20issue%20amongst%20students.%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20issues%20he%20has%20noticed%20are%20born%20broadly%20out%20of%20a%20language%20barrier%2C%20financial%20burden%20and%2For%20a%20lack%20of%20career%20counselling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20a%20girl%20from%20rural%20Bihar%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20come%20here%20but%20was%20sent%20as%20some%20relative%20of%20hers%20had%20cracked%20the%20NEET%20after%20coaching%20in%20Kota.%20She%20was%20bogged%20down%20by%20the%20financial%20and%20familial%20pressure%20of%20it%20all.%20Coming%20from%20a%20Hindi-medium%20school%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20anything.%20She%20felt%20awkward%20in%20the%20hostels%20as%20most%20people%20spoke%20in%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20confided%20in%20her%20parents%20about%20her%20inability%20to%20understand%20what%20was%20being%20taught%20and%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20come%20back%2C%20her%20parents%20heard%20none%20of%20it.%20Singh%20says%20that%20her%20parents%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CEither%20clear%20the%20NEET%20or%20we%20will%20marry%20you%20off%20next%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20burden%20on%20girls%20is%20much%20more%20than%20boys%2C%20according%20to%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20rising%20student%20suicides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoys%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20look%20after%20the%20family%20business%2C%20be%20it%20a%20small%20shop%20or%20a%20farm.%20Girls%20are%20not%20even%20given%20that%20option.%20They%20are%20asked%20to%20clear%20the%20entrance%20or%20threatened%20with%20the%20punishment%20of%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20parents%20must%20tell%20their%20children%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%2C%20and%20to%20let%20them%20choose%20other%20career%20options.%20Telling%20a%20barely%2015-year-old%20child%20that%20one%20exam%20is%20the%20do-all%20of%20their%20life%20leads%20to%20catastrophic%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20child%20will%20try%20and%20reach%20out%20for%20help%20about%20a%20hundred%20times%20before%20they%20take%20that%20step.%20We%20must%20address%20this%20problem%20as%20a%20society%20and%20help%20children%20battle%20depression.%20Everyone%20from%20parents%2C%20teachers%2C%20government%20bodies%20must%20preach%20that%20mental%20health%20is%20as%20important%20as%20physical%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20a%20parent%20or%20teacher%20that%20they%20are%20not%20okay%2C%20one%20must%20address%20it%20immediately%20and%20talk%20to%20them.%20Just%20like%20you%20take%20your%20child%20to%20a%20doctor%20when%20they%20have%20a%20fever%2C%20take%20them%20to%20a%20psychologist%20too%20when%20they%20are%20low%20or%20depressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20student%20spends%2015%20hours%20a%20day%20studying%20in%20Kota%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-238x300.jpeg%20238w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-500x631.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-768x970.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FA-students-room-in-Kota-min-1698068033-150x189.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332823%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221212%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20student%20spends%2015%20hours%20a%20day%20studying%20in%20Kota.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20problems%20faced%20by%20students%20can%20be%20split%20into%20three%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20parental%20expectations%2C%20the%20market%20of%20coaching%20classes%20and%20the%20education%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECompetitive%20exams%20are%2C%20at%20its%20core%2C%20established%20to%20find%20the%20best%20candidate.%20They%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20like%20board%20exams.%20Only%20a%20few%20get%20selected.%20But%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20other%20children%3F%20Do%20we%20speak%20to%20them%20about%20what%20else%20they%20can%20do%3F%20Do%20we%20tell%20them%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54484%2Fstudent-suicide-iit-jee-kota%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudents%20at%20Kota%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20all%20school%20toppers%2C%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20young%20minds%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20not%20used%20to%20failure.%20The%20coaching%20system%20here%20divides%20them%20into%20ranks%20and%20offers%20handsome%20rewards%20to%20the%20toppers.%20They%20use%20children%20as%20a%20commodity%20and%20their%20parents%20put%20all%20their%20hopes%20and%20pressures%20on%20their%20children.%20But%2C%20what%20can%20a%20child%20do%20in%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20having%20a%20capacity%20or%20the%20facility%20to%20handle%20stress%2C%20children%20get%20flustered.%20Even%20adults%20struggle%20with%20managing%20stress%2C%20how%20will%20the%20young%20kids%20fare%20then%3F%20Everyone%20is%20a%20competitor%20and%20the%20parents%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20send%20their%20wards%20to%20Kota%2C%20where%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20have%20very%20high%20fees.%20Different%20reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20Kota%20coaching%20market%20generates%20more%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20crores%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi%20(name%20changed)%20came%20to%20Kota%20in%20June%202023.%20The%2016-year-old%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%20a%20small%20grocery%20store%20in%20Kanpur%20and%20his%20father%20wanted%20him%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20as%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20become%20one.%20He%20was%20raised%20with%20the%20expectations%20of%20studying%20in%20an%20IIT%20and%20being%20the%20harbinger%20of%20hope%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20many%20friends%2C%20he%20says%2C%20and%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20adjust%20to%20this%2024%C3%977%20study%20environment%20where%20relaxation%20is%20hard%20to%20come%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%2