ond-revival-malarvizhli-akka-inspiring-water-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20work%20began%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ranged%20from%20desilting%20and%20rejuvenating%20small%20ponds%2C%20recharging%20borewells%2C%20%3Cem%3Enaali%20kholikaran%20%3C%2Fem%3E(veins%20of%20the%20river%20that%20have%20got%20filled%20with%20silt%20and%20turned%20dry)%20and%20compartment%20bunding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20a%20total%20of%20427%20km%20of%20nullahs%20have%20been%20opened%2C%2019%20ponds%20have%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20life%20and%20a%20total%20of%2079%2C7443%20cubic%20metres%20of%20silt%20has%20been%20removed%20and%20carted%20in%20the%20last%206-7%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20work%20has%20started%20on%20cleaning%20and%20rejuvenating%20the%2020%20km%20Kundalika%20and%20Seena%20river%2C%20of%20which%20around%205%20km%20has%20been%20done%20so%20far%20and%20a%20total%20of%20900%2C000%20lakh%20cubic%20metre%20of%20silt%20and%20a%20total%20of%20405%2C000%20cubic%20metre%20of%20garbage%20has%20been%20pulled%20out%20and%20carted!%20To%20see%20the%20river%20flowing%2C%20even%20if%20only%20in%20part%2C%20gave%20Nutanben%20and%20her%20team%20a%20spark%20of%20joy%20that%20only%20a%20few%20other%20things%20could%20manage!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20perhaps%20only%20joy%20and%20satisfaction%20for%20the%20NGO%20team%20working%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20far%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20community%20living%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaxman%20Sawade%20was%20growing%20around%20five%20quintals%20of%20cotton%20every%20year%20on%20his%20seven%20acre%20farm%20and%20barely%20managing%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20In%202013%2C%20he%20took%20the%20initiative%20of%20applying%20300%20trollies%20of%20silt%20on%20three%20acres%20of%20his%20land.%20Not%20only%20has%20his%20cotton%20output%20gone%20up%2C%20he%20is%20also%20growing%20grapes%20on%20his%20land%20since.%20Overall%2C%20his%20income%20has%20jumped%20to%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20a%20year%2C%20helping%20him%20build%20a%20better%20home%2C%20buy%202.5%20additional%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20a%20tractor%20and%20a%20motorbike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20notion%20that%20almost%20nothing%20brings%20more%20prosperity%20and%20hope%20than%20water%20security%20has%20been%20amply%20reinforced%20by%20Jalna.%20Devkate%20says%20that%20three%20new%20factories%20have%20come%20up%20in%20the%20area%2C%20including%20a%20water%20intensive%20sugarcane%20factory%2C%20leading%20to%20new%20employment%20opportunities%20in%20the%20district.%20In%20a%20region%20that%20has%20been%20bereft%20of%20almost%20any%20work%20opportunities%2C%20this%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20is%20what%20has%20helped%20bring%20in%20more%20and%20more%20takers%20for%20the%20ongoing%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20806px)%20100vw%2C%20806px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20170307_113448_11zon-1697801692.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22806%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20the%20team%20arrived%20in%20the%20district%2C%20villagers%20and%20locals%20were%20highly%20sceptical%20on%20whether%20such%20work%20could%20be%20done%20with%20community%20participation%20and%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20an%20NGO.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20170307_113448_11zon-1697801692.jpg%20806w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20170307_113448_11zon-1697801692-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20170307_113448_11zon-1697801692-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20170307_113448_11zon-1697801692-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F201