2-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F9C20E46F-29E0-4BF4-B138-BC5D6BD19FE6_11zon-1697802292-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F9C20E46F-29E0-4BF4-B138-BC5D6BD19FE6_11zon-1697802292-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F9C20E46F-29E0-4BF4-B138-BC5D6BD19FE6_11zon-1697802292-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332702%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22518%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20were%20allocated%20to%20revive%20the%20scheme%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20and%20over%20100%20NGOs%20were%20pulled%20in%20to%20assist.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIt%20takes%20two%20hands%20to%20clap%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EReaders%20may%20well%20ask%20what%20the%20civil%20society%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20is%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20entire%20funding%20is%20provided%20by%20the%20government.%20And%20the%20answer%20is%20%E2%80%93%20it%20takes%20both%20hands%20to%20clap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20has%20been%20seen%20time%20and%20again%2C%20the%20projects%20that%20work%20best%20are%20those%20where%20the%20private%20and%20public%20sector%20come%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20former%20NITI%20Aayog%20official.%20He%20says%20that%20the%20private%20or%20civil%20society%20players%20bring%20efficiencies%20and%20levels%20of%20competence%20that%20government%20players%20often%20lack.%20Chandra%20echoes%20this%20sentiment%20in%20reverse%20by%20saying%20that%20the%20scale%20government%20can%20provide%2C%20no%20private%20sector%20player%20can%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20even%20while%20the%20state%20government%20is%20willing%20to%20finance%20almost%20the%20entire%20effort%2C%20the%20A.T.E.%20CF%20identifies%2C%20monitors%20and%20assists%20the%20NGOs%20that%20work%20on%20the%20groun